<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>PCV Site Selection Tool — Power Curve Verification</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --sky1:#0b1f3a;--sky2:#0e3460;--sky3:#1a5f8a;
  --sky4:#2d9cce;--sky5:#87ceeb;
  --mint:#1db87e;--gold:#f0a500;
  --white:#fff;--border:rgba(255,255,255,.12);
  --display:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif;
  --body:'Open Sans',sans-serif;
}
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:var(--body);color:var(--white);background:linear-gradient(160deg,var(--sky1) 0%,var(--sky2) 40%,var(--sky3) 75%,#0a4a6e 100%);min-height:100vh}
.back-link{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);text-decoration:none;padding:.7rem 1.4rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);transition:color .25s}
.back-link:hover{color:var(--mint)}
.back-link svg{width:14px;height:14px}
.tool-header{padding:1.5rem 2rem 0;max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto}
.tool-title{font-family:var(--display);font-size:clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2.2rem);font-weight:400;font-style:italic;color:#fff;margin-bottom:.3rem}
.tool-title span{color:var(--mint)}
.tool-subtitle{font-size:.78rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);font-weight:300;letter-spacing:.06em}
.stepper{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:0;padding:1.5rem 1rem;max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;flex-wrap:wrap}
.step-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;padding:.5rem .8rem;cursor:pointer;border-radius:8px;transition:background .25s;user-select:none}
.step-item:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.04)}
.step-item.active{background:rgba(29,184,126,.1)}
.step-num{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:.7rem;font-weight:800;border:2px solid var(--border);color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);transition:all .3s;flex-shrink:0}
.step-item.active .step-num{background:var(--mint);border-color:var(--mint);color:var(--sky1)}
.step-item.done .step-num{background:rgba(29,184,126,.3);border-color:var(--mint);color:var(--mint)}
.step-label{font-size:.68rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);transition:color .25s;white-space:nowrap}
.step-item.active .step-label{color:var(--mint)}
.step-item.done .step-label{color:rgba(255,255,255,.55)}
.step-connector{width:24px;height:2px;background:var(--border);flex-shrink:0;border-radius:1px}
.main-container{max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.5rem 3rem}
.step-panel{display:none;animation:fadeIn .4s ease}
.step-panel.active{display:block}
@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
.card{background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:1.8rem;margin-bottom:1.2rem}
.card-title{font-size:.68rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);margin-bottom:1rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem}
.card-title::after{content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border)}
.upload-zone{border:2px dashed var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:1.5rem;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;transition:border-color .3s,background .3s;background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);position:relative}
.upload-zone:hover{border-color:var(--mint);background:rgba(29,184,126,.04)}
.upload-zone input{position:absolute;inset:0;opacity:0;cursor:pointer}
.upload-zone.loaded{border-color:var(--mint);border-style:solid;background:rgba(29,184,126,.06)}
.upload-zone.error{border-color:#e74c3c;border-style:solid;background:rgba(231,76,60,.06)}
.upload-icon{font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:.3rem;display:block;opacity:.5}
.upload-text{font-size:.78rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);font-weight:300}
.upload-hint{font-size:.6rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.25);margin-top:.25rem}
.upload-info{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem;padding:.3rem 0;flex-wrap:wrap}
.upload-check{font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--mint);flex-shrink:0}
.upload-filename{font-size:.78rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);font-weight:600}
.upload-meta{font-size:.62rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4)}
.btn{font-family:var(--body);font-size:.7rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;border:none;padding:.7rem 1.6rem;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .25s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem}
.btn-primary{background:var(--mint);color:var(--sky1)}
.btn-primary:hover{background:var(--gold);transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(240,165,0,.25)}
.btn-secondary{background:none;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);border:1.5px solid var(--border)}
.btn-secondary:hover{border-color:var(--mint);color:var(--mint)}
.btn-sm{padding:.4rem .9rem;font-size:.6rem}
.btn-danger{background:rgba(231,76,60,.15);color:#e74c3c;border:1px solid rgba(231,76,60,.3)}
.btn-danger:hover{background:rgba(231,76,60,.25)}
.grid-2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1.2rem}
.grid-3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:1rem}
.grid-4{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1px;background:var(--border);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden}
.flex-row{display:flex;gap:1.2rem;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:stretch}
.flex-col{flex:1;min-width:260px}
.form-group{margin-bottom:1rem}
.form-label{display:block;font-size:.58rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);margin-bottom:.35rem}
.form-input,.form-select{width:100%;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;font-family:var(--body);font-size:.82rem;color:#fff;padding:.55rem .8rem;outline:none;transition:border-color .25s}
.form-input:focus,.form-select:focus{border-color:var(--mint)}
.form-select option{background:var(--sky1);color:#fff}
.form-row{display:flex;gap:.8rem;align-items:end}
.form-row .form-group{flex:1}
.metric-item{padding:1.1rem;background:rgba(11,31,58,.8);text-align:center}
.metric-val{display:block;font-family:var(--display);font-size:1.8rem;font-style:italic;color:var(--mint);line-height:1}
.metric-val.warn{color:var(--gold)}.metric-val.bad{color:#e74c3c}
.metric-label{display:block;font-size:.55rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);margin-top:.25rem}
.table-wrap{max-height:400px;overflow-y:auto;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px}
.table-wrap::-webkit-scrollbar{width:6px}
.table-wrap::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)}
.table-wrap::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);border-radius:3px}
table.data-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:.75rem}
table.data-table th{text-align:left;font-size:.58rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);padding:.6rem .7rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);white-space:nowrap;position:sticky;top:0;background:var(--sky1);z-index:1}
table.data-table td{padding:.5rem .7rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.04);color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);font-weight:300}
table.data-table tr:hover td{background:rgba(29,184,126,.04)}
.badge{display:inline-block;font-size:.55rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:.15rem .5rem;border-radius:4px}
.badge-valid{background:rgba(29,184,126,.15);color:var(--mint);border:1px solid rgba(29,184,126,.3)}
.badge-invalid{background:rgba(231,76,60,.15);color:#e74c3c;border:1px solid rgba(231,76,60,.3)}
.badge-warn{background:rgba(240,165,0,.15);color:var(--gold);border:1px solid rgba(240,165,0,.3)}
.badge-free{background:rgba(45,156,206,.15);color:var(--sky4);border:1px solid rgba(45,156,206,.3)}
.badge-first{background:rgba(29,184,126,.2);color:var(--mint);border:1px solid rgba(29,184,126,.4)}
.badge-prop{background:rgba(240,165,0,.15);color:var(--gold);border:1px solid rgba(240,165,0,.3)}
.canvas-wrap{background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;position:relative}
.canvas-wrap canvas{display:block;width:100%;height:auto}
.alert{padding:.9rem 1.1rem;border-radius:8px;font-size:.78rem;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:3px solid}
.alert-info{background:rgba(45,156,206,.08);border-color:var(--sky4);color:rgba(255,255,255,.7)}
.alert-success{background:rgba(29,184,126,.08);border-color:var(--mint);color:rgba(255,255,255,.7)}
.alert-error{background:rgba(231,76,60,.08);border-color:#e74c3c;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7)}
.alert-warning{background:rgba(240,165,0,.08);border-color:var(--gold);color:rgba(255,255,255,.7)}
.progress{height:4px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden;margin-top:.4rem}
.progress-bar{height:100%;border-radius:2px;transition:width .5s;background:var(--mint)}
.tabs{display:flex;gap:.2rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding-bottom:0;margin-bottom:1.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
.tab{font-size:.65rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);padding:.6rem 1rem;cursor:pointer;border:none;background:none;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;transition:color .25s,border-color .25s;font-family:var(--body)}
.tab:hover{color:rgba(255,255,255,.7)}
.tab.active{color:var(--mint);border-bottom-color:var(--mint)}
.tab-panel{display:none;animation:fadeIn .3s ease}
.tab-panel.active{display:block}
.wind-rose-container{display:flex;gap:1.5rem;align-items:flex-start;flex-wrap:wrap}
.wind-rose-wrap{flex-shrink:0}
.wind-rose-info{flex:1;min-width:240px}
.pred-dir-box{background:rgba(29,184,126,.08);border:1px solid rgba(29,184,126,.3);border-radius:10px;padding:1.1rem 1.3rem;margin-bottom:.8rem}
.pred-dir-value{font-family:var(--display);font-size:1.8rem;font-style:italic;color:var(--mint);line-height:1}
.pred-dir-label{font-size:.55rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);margin-top:.2rem;display:block}
.stat-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:.5rem}
.stat-item{padding:.6rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px}
.stat-val{display:block;font-family:var(--display);font-size:1.2rem;font-style:italic;color:var(--sky4);line-height:1}
.stat-lbl{display:block;font-size:.48rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3);margin-top:.15rem}
.score-bar{height:6px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden;margin-top:.25rem}
.score-fill{height:100%;border-radius:3px;transition:width .6s;background:var(--mint)}
.score-fill.gold{background:var(--gold)}
.score-fill.red{background:#e74c3c}
.report-content{background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:2rem;max-height:600px;overflow-y:auto;font-size:.82rem;line-height:1.7}
.report-content h3{font-family:var(--display);font-size:1.1rem;font-style:italic;color:#fff;margin:1.2rem 0 .6rem;padding-bottom:.4rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.report-content h3:first-child{margin-top:0}
.report-content p,.report-content li{color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);font-weight:300}
.report-content table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:.6rem 0;font-size:.75rem}
.report-content th{background:rgba(29,184,126,.1);font-size:.58rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);padding:.45rem .55rem;text-align:left;border:1px solid var(--border)}
.report-content td{padding:.35rem .55rem;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);font-weight:300}
.loading-overlay{position:absolute;inset:0;background:rgba(11,31,58,.85);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index:10;border-radius:10px;backdrop-filter:blur(4px);gap:.8rem}
.loading-text{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--mint);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.08em;animation:pulse 1.5s ease infinite}
.loading-spinner{width:32px;height:32px;border:3px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-top-color:var(--mint);border-radius:50%;animation:spin .8s linear infinite}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:.6}50%{opacity:1}}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
.manual-entry{display:none;margin-top:1rem}
.manual-entry.show{display:block}
.manual-row{display:flex;gap:.5rem;align-items:center;margin-bottom:.5rem}
.manual-row input{flex:1}
.nav-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-top:1.5rem}
@media(max-width:900px){
  .grid-2,.grid-3{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .grid-4{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
  .stepper{gap:0;padding:1rem .5rem}
  .step-connector{display:none}
  .flex-row{flex-direction:column}
  .form-row{flex-direction:column}
  .wind-rose-container{flex-direction:column;align-items:center}
}
@media(max-width:600px){
  .grid-4{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .step-label{display:none}
  .tool-header{padding:1rem 1rem 0}
  .main-container{padding:0 1rem 2rem}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<a class="back-link" href="https://kvelmurugan77.github.io/portfolio/">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
  Back to Portfolio
</a>

<div class="tool-header">
  <h1 class="tool-title">PCV <span>Site Selection</span> Tool</h1>
  <p class="tool-subtitle">IEC 61400-12-1 Mast Location Proposal &amp; WTG Selection — windPRO-Style Analysis</p>
</div>

<!-- Step Wizard -->
<div class="stepper" id="stepper">
  <div class="step-item active" data-step="1" onclick="goToStep(1)">
    <div class="step-num">1</div>
    <span class="step-label">Layout</span>
  </div>
  <div class="step-connector"></div>
  <div class="step-item" data-step="2" onclick="goToStep(2)">
    <div class="step-num">2</div>
    <span class="step-label">Wind Data</span>
  </div>
  <div class="step-connector"></div>
  <div class="step-item" data-step="3" onclick="goToStep(3)">
    <div class="step-num">3</div>
    <span class="step-label">Wind Rose</span>
  </div>
  <div class="step-connector"></div>
  <div class="step-item" data-step="4" onclick="goToStep(4)">
    <div class="step-num">4</div>
    <span class="step-label">Visualize</span>
  </div>
  <div class="step-connector"></div>
  <div class="step-item" data-step="5" onclick="goToStep(5)">
    <div class="step-num">5</div>
    <span class="step-label">Mast Proposal</span>
  </div>
  <div class="step-connector"></div>
  <div class="step-item" data-step="6" onclick="goToStep(6)">
    <div class="step-num">6</div>
    <span class="step-label">Report</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="main-container">

<!-- ====================== STEP 1: SITE LAYOUT ====================== -->
<div class="step-panel active" id="step1">
  <div class="alert alert-info">This tool proposes optimal met mast locations for Power Curve Verification per IEC 61400-12-1. Upload your wind farm layout to begin.</div>
  <div style="display:flex;gap:.6rem;align-items:center;margin-bottom:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap">
    <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="loadDemoLayout()">🎬 Load Demo Data</button>
    <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" onclick="clearAll()">🗑 Clear All</button>
  </div>
  <div class="grid-2">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Target WTG Layout (Required)</div>
      <div class="upload-zone" id="wtgUploadZone">
        <input type="file" accept=".csv,.txt" id="wtgFileInput" onchange="handleWTGUpload(event)">
        <span class="upload-icon">⚡</span>
        <span class="upload-text">Upload WTG Layout CSV</span>
        <span class="upload-hint">Columns: id, x/latitude, y/longitude, rd (rotor diameter), hh (hub height)</span>
        <div class="upload-info" id="wtgUploadInfo" style="display:none"></div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" style="margin-top:.6rem" onclick="toggleManual('wtgManual')">+ Manual Entry</button>
      <div class="manual-entry" id="wtgManual">
        <div class="manual-row"><input class="form-input" placeholder="ID" id="wId"><input class="form-input" type="number" placeholder="X/Lat" id="wX"><input class="form-input" type="number" placeholder="Y/Lon" id="wY"><input class="form-input" type="number" placeholder="RD (m)" id="wRD"><input class="form-input" type="number" placeholder="HH (m)" id="wHH"><button class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" onclick="addManualWTG()">Add</button></div>
      </div>
      <div class="table-wrap" id="wtgTableWrap" style="margin-top:.8rem"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">External WTG — Neighboring Farm (Optional)</div>
      <div class="upload-zone" id="extUploadZone">
        <input type="file" accept=".csv,.txt" id="extFileInput" onchange="handleExtUpload(event)">
        <span class="upload-icon">🏭</span>
        <span class="upload-text">Upload External WTG CSV</span>
        <span class="upload-hint">Same format as WTG CSV. Neighboring farm WTGs that cause wake effects.</span>
        <div class="upload-info" id="extUploadInfo" style="display:none"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="table-wrap" id="extTableWrap" style="margin-top:.8rem"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:.5rem">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Terrain Map .map / .xyz File (Optional)</div>
      <div class="upload-zone" id="mapUploadZone">
        <input type="file" accept=".map,.csv,.txt,.xyz" id="mapFileInput" onchange="handleMapUpload(event)">
        <span class="upload-icon">🏔</span>
        <span class="upload-text">Upload .map / .xyz / elevation CSV</span>
        <span class="upload-hint">WAsP map format, .xyz, or x,y,elevation CSV. Synthetic terrain used if not provided.</span>
        <div class="upload-info" id="mapUploadInfo" style="display:none"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">IEC 61400-12-1 Analysis Configuration</div>
      <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label">IEC Standard</label><select class="form-select" id="cfgIEC"><option value="2017">IEC 61400-12-1:2017 (Ed.2)</option><option value="2005">IEC 61400-12-1:2005 (Ed.1)</option></select></div>
      <div class="form-row">
        <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label">Sector Width</label><select class="form-select" id="cfgSector"><option value="10">10° (36 sectors)</option><option value="20">20° (18 sectors)</option></select></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label">Assessment Radius (m)</label><input class="form-input" type="number" id="cfgRadius" value="5000"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-row">
        <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label">Min Mast-WTG Dist (D)</label><input class="form-input" type="number" id="cfgMinDist" value="2" step="0.5"></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label">Wake Angular Thresh (°)</label><input class="form-input" type="number" id="cfgWakeAng" value="30"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-row">
        <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label">Wake Dist Threshold (D)</label><input class="form-input" type="number" id="cfgWakeDist" value="20"></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label">Min Free Sector (°)</label><input class="form-input" type="number" id="cfgMinFree" value="20"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-row">
    <div></div>
    <button class="btn btn-primary" id="step1Next" onclick="goToStep(2)" disabled>Next: Wind Data →</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ====================== STEP 2: WIND DATA (optional) ====================== -->
<div class="step-panel" id="step2">
  <div class="alert alert-info">Upload your own wind data, or let the tool auto-download ERA5T reanalysis data based on your wind farm location. If you skip this step, ERA5T will be downloaded automatically.</div>
  <div class="grid-2">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Upload Wind Data CSV</div>
      <div class="upload-zone" id="windUploadZone">
        <input type="file" accept=".csv,.txt" id="windFileInput" onchange="handleWindUpload(event)">
        <span class="upload-icon">📁</span>
        <span class="upload-text">Click or drag CSV file here</span>
        <span class="upload-hint">Columns: timestamp, windspeed, winddirection</span>
        <div class="upload-info" id="windUploadInfo" style="display:none"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Download ERA5T Reanalysis (Free, No API Key)</div>
      <div class="alert alert-warning" id="era5CoordNote" style="display:none">WTG layout uses UTM coordinates. Please enter geographic lat/lon manually for ERA5 download.</div>
      <div class="form-row">
        <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label">Latitude</label><input class="form-input" type="number" step="0.001" id="era5Lat" value="" placeholder="Auto-detected from layout"></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label">Longitude</label><input class="form-input" type="number" step="0.001" id="era5Lon" value="" placeholder="Auto-detected from layout"></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label">Year</label><select class="form-select" id="era5Year"><option value="2023">2023</option><option value="2022">2022</option><option value="2021">2021</option><option value="2020">2020</option><option value="2019">2019</option></select></div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:.6rem;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:.5rem">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="downloadERA5()">⬇ Download ERA5T</button>
        <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" onclick="loadDemoWindData()">🎬 Demo Data</button>
      </div>
      <div id="era5Status" style="margin-top:.8rem"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-row">
    <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="goToStep(1)">← Back: Layout</button>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:.6rem">
      <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="skipWindData()">Skip (Auto-Download ERA5) →</button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" id="step2Next" onclick="goToStep(3)">Next: Wind Rose →</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ====================== STEP 3: WIND ROSE ====================== -->
<div class="step-panel" id="step3">
  <div class="alert alert-warning" id="noWindAlert" style="display:none">No wind data loaded. Please go back and upload or download wind data first.</div>
  <div id="windRoseSection" style="display:none">
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Wind Rose (36 Sectors, 10° each)</div>
        <div class="wind-rose-container">
          <div class="wind-rose-wrap"><div class="canvas-wrap"><canvas id="windRoseCanvas" width="460" height="460"></canvas></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="wind-rose-info">
        <div class="pred-dir-box"><div class="pred-dir-value" id="predDirValue">—</div><div class="pred-dir-label">Predominant Wind Direction (FROM)</div></div>
        <div class="stat-grid">
          <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-val" id="statMeanSpeed">—</span><span class="stat-lbl">Mean Speed (m/s)</span></div>
          <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-val" id="statMaxSpeed">—</span><span class="stat-lbl">Max Speed (m/s)</span></div>
          <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-val" id="statPredFreq">—</span><span class="stat-lbl">Pred. Dir. Freq</span></div>
          <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-val" id="statCalmHours">—</span><span class="stat-lbl">Calm Hours</span></div>
          <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-val" id="statRecords">—</span><span class="stat-lbl">Total Records</span></div>
          <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-val" id="statWeibullK">—</span><span class="stat-lbl">Weibull K</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" style="margin-top:1rem">
      <div class="card-title">Sector Frequency Table</div>
      <div class="table-wrap" id="sectorTableWrap"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-row">
    <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="goToStep(2)">← Back: Wind Data</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary" id="step3Next" onclick="goToStep(4)">Next: Visualize →</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ====================== STEP 4: LAYOUT VISUALIZATION ====================== -->
<div class="step-panel" id="step4">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">Site Layout Map — First-Row WTG Identification</div>
    <div class="canvas-wrap" style="position:relative">
      <canvas id="layoutCanvas" width="1200" height="700"></canvas>
      <div class="loading-overlay" id="layoutLoading" style="display:none"><div class="loading-spinner"></div><div class="loading-text">Rendering layout...</div></div>
    </div>
    <div id="layoutLegend" style="display:flex;gap:1.2rem;margin-top:.8rem;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="card" style="margin-top:.5rem">
    <div class="card-title">Layout Summary</div>
    <div class="grid-4" id="layoutMetrics"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-row">
    <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="goToStep(3)">← Back: Wind Rose</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="goToStep(5)">Next: Mast Proposal →</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ====================== STEP 5: MAST PROPOSAL & ANALYSIS ====================== -->
<div class="step-panel" id="step5">
  <div style="display:flex;gap:.6rem;align-items:center;margin-bottom:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap">
    <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="runFullAnalysis()" id="runAnalysisBtn">🚀 Propose Mast Locations</button>
    <span style="font-size:.68rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);font-weight:300">Automatically identifies optimal met mast positions per IEC 61400-12-1</span>
  </div>
  <div id="analysisProgress" style="display:none"><div class="progress"><div class="progress-bar" id="analysisProgressBar" style="width:0%"></div></div><div id="analysisStatusText" style="font-size:.7rem;color:var(--mint);margin-top:.4rem">Analyzing...</div></div>
  <div id="analysisAlerts"></div>
  <div id="analysisResults" style="display:none">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Proposal Summary</div>
      <div class="grid-4" id="proposalMetrics"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:.5rem">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">First-Row WTG Assessment</div>
        <div class="table-wrap" id="firstRowTable"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Proposed Mast Locations (Ranked)</div>
        <div class="table-wrap" id="mastProposalTable"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" style="margin-top:.5rem">
      <div class="card-title">1-Mast-to-N-WTG Configurations</div>
      <div class="table-wrap" id="configTable"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" style="margin-top:.5rem">
      <div class="card-title">Recommendations</div>
      <div id="recommendations"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-row">
    <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="goToStep(4)">← Back: Visualize</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary" id="step5Next" onclick="goToStep(6)" disabled>Next: Detailed Report →</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ====================== STEP 6: DETAILED REPORT ====================== -->
<div class="step-panel" id="step6">
  <div id="noAnalysisAlert" class="alert alert-warning" style="display:none">Please run the mast proposal analysis in Step 5 first.</div>
  <div id="reportSection" style="display:none">
    <div class="tabs" id="reportTabs">
      <button class="tab active" onclick="switchReportTab('terrain')">Terrain &amp; Measurement Sectors</button>
      <button class="tab" onclick="switchReportTab('freestream')">Freestream Analysis</button>
      <button class="tab" onclick="switchReportTab('report')">DNV-Style Report</button>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-panel active" id="tab-terrain">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Select Proposed Mast–WTG Pair</div>
        <div class="form-group"><select class="form-select" id="terrainPairSelect" onchange="renderTerrainDetail()"></select></div>
        <div class="grid-2">
          <div class="canvas-wrap"><canvas id="terrainPolarCanvas" width="460" height="460"></canvas></div>
          <div>
            <div class="card-title">Sector Details</div>
            <div class="table-wrap" id="terrainSectorTable" style="max-height:380px"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="margin-top:1rem">
          <div class="card-title">Terrain Profile — Selected Sector</div>
          <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label">View Direction (°)</label><select class="form-select" id="profileDirSelect" onchange="renderTerrainDetail()"></select></div>
          <div class="canvas-wrap"><canvas id="terrainProfileCanvas" width="1100" height="300"></canvas></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-panel" id="tab-freestream">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Wake Impact Assessment</div>
        <div class="grid-2">
          <div class="canvas-wrap"><canvas id="wakeRoseCanvas" width="460" height="460"></canvas></div>
          <div>
            <div class="card-title">Freestream Summary</div>
            <div class="stat-grid" id="freestreamStats"></div>
            <div class="table-wrap" id="wakeSectorTable" style="max-height:300px;margin-top:.8rem"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-panel" id="tab-report">
      <div style="display:flex;gap:.6rem;margin-bottom:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="generateReport()">📄 Generate DNV-Style Report</button>
        <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="window.print()">🖨 Print / Export PDF</button>
      </div>
      <div class="report-content" id="reportContent">
        <div class="alert alert-info">Click "Generate DNV-Style Report" to create the comprehensive site suitability report.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-row">
    <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="goToStep(5)">← Back: Mast Proposal</button>
  </div>
</div>

</div><!-- end main-container -->

<script>
// ============================================================================
// PCV MAST LOCATION PROPOSAL TOOL — IEC 61400-12-1 windPRO-Style Engine
// ============================================================================

const STATE = {
  wtgs: [],
  extWtgs: [],
  terrainPoints: [],
  windData: [],
  windRoseData: null,
  proposedMasts: [],
  analysisResults: null,
  currentStep: 1,
  hasMapData: false,
  layoutCentroid: null
};

// ── NAVIGATION ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
function goToStep(n) {
  if (n === 2 && STATE.wtgs.length === 0) { alert('Please load at least one WTG in Step 1.'); return; }
  if (n === 3 && STATE.windData.length === 0) { alert('No wind data loaded. Please go to Step 2 to upload or download wind data.'); return; }
  if (n === 4 && STATE.wtgs.length === 0) { alert('Please load WTG layout first.'); return; }

  STATE.currentStep = n;
  document.querySelectorAll('.step-panel').forEach(p => p.classList.remove('active'));
  document.querySelectorAll('.step-item').forEach(s => { s.classList.remove('active'); const sn = parseInt(s.dataset.step); if (sn < n) s.classList.add('done'); else s.classList.remove('done'); });
  const panel = document.getElementById('step' + n);
  if (panel) panel.classList.add('active');
  const stepItem = document.querySelector(`.step-item[data-step="${n}"]`);
  if (stepItem) stepItem.classList.add('active');
  if (n === 2) autoFillERA5();
  if (n === 3) renderWindRose();
  if (n === 4) renderLayout();
}

function markStepDone(n) { const el = document.querySelector(`.step-item[data-step="${n}"]`); if (el) el.classList.add('done'); }

// ── HELPERS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
function setUploadStatus(zoneId, infoId, status, text, meta) {
  const zone = document.getElementById(zoneId), info = document.getElementById(infoId);
  zone.classList.remove('loaded', 'error');
  if (status === 'loaded') zone.classList.add('loaded'); else if (status === 'error') zone.classList.add('error');
  if (text) { info.style.display = 'flex'; info.innerHTML = `<span class="upload-check">${status === 'loaded' ? '✅' : '❌'}</span><span class="upload-filename">${text}</span>${meta ? `<span class="upload-meta">${meta}</span>` : ''}`; }
  else { info.style.display = 'none'; }
}

function parseCSV(text) {
  const lines = text.trim().split(/\r?\n/); if (lines.length < 2) return { headers: [], rows: [] };
  const delimiter = lines[0].includes('\t') ? '\t' : ',';
  const headers = lines[0].split(delimiter).map(h => h.trim().replace(/^["']|["']$/g, '').toLowerCase().replace(/[^a-z0-9]/g, ''));
  const rows = [];
  for (let i = 1; i < lines.length; i++) { const vals = lines[i].split(delimiter).map(v => v.trim().replace(/^["']|["']$/g, '')); if (vals.length >= headers.length) { const row = {}; headers.forEach((h, j) => row[h] = vals[j]); rows.push(row); } }
  return { headers, rows };
}

function findColVal(headers, vals, patterns) { for (const p of patterns) { const idx = headers.findIndex(h => h.includes(p)); if (idx >= 0 && idx < vals.length) return vals[idx]; } return ''; }
function toggleManual(id) { document.getElementById(id).classList.toggle('show'); }
function degToCompass(d) { const dirs = ['N','NNE','NE','ENE','E','ESE','SE','SSE','S','SSW','SW','WSW','W','WNW','NW','NNW']; return dirs[Math.round(d / 22.5) % 16]; }

// ── GEO UTILITIES ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
const EARTH_R = 6371000;
function haversine(lat1, lon1, lat2, lon2) { const toRad = d => d * Math.PI / 180; const dLat = toRad(lat2 - lat1), dLon = toRad(lon2 - lon1); const a = Math.sin(dLat / 2) ** 2 + Math.cos(toRad(lat1)) * Math.cos(toRad(lat2)) * Math.sin(dLon / 2) ** 2; return EARTH_R * 2 * Math.atan2(Math.sqrt(a), Math.sqrt(1 - a)); }
function calcBearing(lat1, lon1, lat2, lon2) { const toRad = d => d * Math.PI / 180, toDeg = r => r * 180 / Math.PI; const dLon = toRad(lon2 - lon1); const y = Math.sin(dLon) * Math.cos(toRad(lat2)); const x = Math.cos(toRad(lat1)) * Math.sin(toRad(lat2)) - Math.sin(toRad(lat1)) * Math.cos(toRad(lat2)) * Math.cos(dLon); return ((toDeg(Math.atan2(y, x)) % 360) + 360) % 360; }
function angularDev(a, b) { let d = Math.abs(a - b); return d > 180 ? 360 - d : d; }
function destPoint(lat, lon, bearing, dist) { const toRad = d => d * Math.PI / 180, toDeg = r => r * 180 / Math.PI; const dR = dist / EARTH_R; const lat1 = toRad(lat), lon1 = toRad(lon), brng = toRad(bearing); const lat2 = Math.asin(Math.sin(lat1) * Math.cos(dR) + Math.cos(lat1) * Math.sin(dR) * Math.cos(brng)); const lon2 = lon1 + Math.atan2(Math.sin(brng) * Math.sin(dR) * Math.cos(lat1), Math.cos(dR) - Math.sin(lat1) * Math.sin(lat2)); return { lat: toDeg(lat2), lon: toDeg(lon2) }; }
function isGeo(lat, lon) { return Math.abs(lat) <= 90 && Math.abs(lon) <= 180; }
function getDist(a, b) { return (isGeo(a.lat, a.lon) && isGeo(b.lat, b.lon)) ? haversine(a.lat, a.lon, b.lat, b.lon) : Math.sqrt((a.lat - b.lat) ** 2 + (a.lon - b.lon) ** 2); }
function getBearing(a, b) { return (isGeo(a.lat, a.lon) && isGeo(b.lat, b.lon)) ? calcBearing(a.lat, a.lon, b.lat, b.lon) : ((Math.atan2(b.lon - a.lon, b.lat - a.lat) * 180 / Math.PI) + 360) % 360; }

// ── TERRAIN ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
function synthElev(x, y, base) {
  base = base || 850;
  const hash = (a, b, s) => { let h = s + a * 374761393 + b * 668265263; h = ((h ^ (h >> 13)) * 1274126177) | 0; return ((h ^ (h >> 16)) & 0x7fffffff) / 0x7fffffff; };
  const sm = t => t * t * (3 - 2 * t);
  const vn = (px, py, seed) => { const ix = Math.floor(px), iy = Math.floor(py); const fx = sm(px - ix), fy = sm(py - iy); return (hash(ix, iy, seed) * (1 - fx) + hash(ix + 1, iy, seed) * fx) * (1 - fy) + (hash(ix, iy + 1, seed) * (1 - fx) + hash(ix + 1, iy + 1, seed) * fx) * fy; };
  const sx = x * 0.00002, sy = y * 0.00002;
  return base + ((vn(sx, sy, 42) + vn(sx * 2, sy * 2, 100) * 0.5 + vn(sx * 4, sy * 4, 200) * 0.25) / 1.75 - 0.5) * 40;
}

function generateTerrainProfile(origin, bearing, maxDist, step, terrainPts) {
  const profile = [], baseElev = synthElev(origin.lat, origin.lon);
  for (let d = step; d <= maxDist; d += step) {
    let elev;
    if (terrainPts && terrainPts.length > 0 && terrainPts[0].z !== 0) { elev = interpElev(origin, bearing, d, terrainPts, baseElev); }
    else { const pt = isGeo(origin.lat, origin.lon) ? destPoint(origin.lat, origin.lon, bearing, d) : { lat: origin.lat + d * Math.sin(bearing * Math.PI / 180), lon: origin.lon + d * Math.cos(bearing * Math.PI / 180) }; elev = synthElev(pt.lat, pt.lon); }
    const prev = profile.length > 0 ? profile[profile.length - 1].elev : baseElev;
    const slope = d > step ? ((elev - prev) / step) * 100 : 0;
    profile.push({ dist: d, elev, slope });
  }
  return profile;
}

function interpElev(origin, bearing, dist, pts, fallback) {
  let tLat, tLon;
  if (isGeo(origin.lat, origin.lon)) { const pt = destPoint(origin.lat, origin.lon, bearing, dist); tLat = pt.lat; tLon = pt.lon; }
  else { tLat = origin.lat + dist * Math.sin(bearing * Math.PI / 180); tLon = origin.lon + dist * Math.cos(bearing * Math.PI / 180); }
  const dists = pts.map(p => { const d = Math.sqrt((p.x - tLat) ** 2 + (p.y - tLon) ** 2); return { elev: p.z, d: Math.max(d, 1) }; }).sort((a, b) => a.d - b.d).slice(0, 5);
  let wSum = 0, eSum = 0; for (const p of dists) { const w = 1 / (p.d * p.d); wSum += w; eSum += p.elev * w; }
  return wSum > 0 ? eSum / wSum : fallback;
}

// ── TERRAIN ASSESSMENT (per IEC 61400-12-1) ─────────────────────────────────
function performTerrainAssessment(mast, wtg, allWtgs, extWtgs, terrainPts, config) {
  const dist = getDist(mast, wtg), distD = dist / wtg.rd;
  const bearingMW = getBearing(mast, wtg);
  const numSectors = 360 / config.sectorWidth;
  const sectors = [];
  for (let i = 0; i < numSectors; i++) {
    const dir = i * config.sectorWidth;
    const profile = generateTerrainProfile(mast, dir, config.assessmentRadius, 50, terrainPts);
    const slopes = profile.map(p => Math.abs(p.slope));
    const maxSlope = slopes.length > 0 ? Math.max(...slopes) : 0;
    const maxSlopeDeg = Math.atan(maxSlope / 100) * 180 / Math.PI;
    const wakeAffected = [];
    const allW = [...allWtgs, ...(extWtgs || [])];
    for (const w of allW) {
      if (w.id === wtg.id) continue;
      const wBearing = getBearing(mast, w); const aDev = angularDev(dir, wBearing);
      const wDist = getDist(mast, w); const wDistD = wDist / (w.rd || wtg.rd);
      if (aDev <= config.wakeAngularThreshold / 2 && wDistD <= config.wakeDistanceThresholdD) wakeAffected.push(w.name);
    }
    const isFreestream = wakeAffected.length === 0;
    const simplePass = maxSlopeDeg <= 3; const complexPass = maxSlopeDeg <= 10;
    let terrainClass = simplePass ? 'A' : complexPass ? 'B' : 'S';
    const isValid = complexPass && isFreestream;
    const failures = [];
    if (!simplePass && !complexPass) failures.push(`Slope ${maxSlopeDeg.toFixed(1)}° exceeds threshold`);
    if (!isFreestream) failures.push(`Wake: ${wakeAffected.join(', ')}`);
    sectors.push({ dir, maxSlopeDeg, isFreestream, wakeAffected, terrainClass, isValid, failures, simplePass, complexPass, profile });
  }
  const validSectors = sectors.filter(s => s.isValid);
  const freestreamSectors = sectors.filter(s => s.isFreestream);
  const overallClass = sectors.some(s => s.terrainClass === 'S') ? 'S' : sectors.some(s => s.terrainClass === 'B') ? 'B' : 'A';
  return { mastId: mast.id, mastName: mast.name, wtgId: wtg.id, wtgName: wtg.name, distance: dist, distanceD: distD, bearing: bearingMW, sectors, numSectors, validSectors: validSectors.map(s => s.dir), validCount: validSectors.length, freestreamCount: freestreamSectors.length, terrainClass: overallClass, validPct: (validSectors.length / numSectors * 100), isCompliant: validSectors.length >= numSectors * 0.25 };
}

// ── STEP 1: LAYOUT UPLOAD ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
function handleWTGUpload(e) {
  const file = e.target.files[0]; if (!file) return;
  const reader = new FileReader();
  reader.onload = function(ev) {
    try {
      const { headers, rows } = parseCSV(ev.target.result); STATE.wtgs = []; let count = 0;
      for (let i = 0; i < rows.length; i++) {
        const row = rows[i], vals = Object.values(row);
        const id = findColVal(headers, vals, ['id', 'name', 'wtg', 'turbine']);
        const x = parseFloat(findColVal(headers, vals, ['lat', 'latitude', 'x', 'easting']));
        const y = parseFloat(findColVal(headers, vals, ['lon', 'longitude', 'y', 'northing']));
        const rd = parseFloat(findColVal(headers, vals, ['rd', 'rotordiameter', 'rotor', 'diameter']));
        const hh = parseFloat(findColVal(headers, vals, ['hh', 'hubheight', 'hub']));
        if (!isNaN(x) && !isNaN(y) && !isNaN(rd) && !isNaN(hh)) { STATE.wtgs.push({ id: id || `W${count + 1}`, name: id || `WTG-${String(count + 1).padStart(2, '0')}`, lat: x, lon: y, rd, hh }); count++; }
      }
      if (count === 0) throw new Error('No valid WTG records found');
      setUploadStatus('wtgUploadZone', 'wtgUploadInfo', 'loaded', file.name, `${count} WTGs loaded`);
      renderWTGTable(); calcCentroid(); checkStep1Ready();
    } catch (err) { setUploadStatus('wtgUploadZone', 'wtgUploadInfo', 'error', file.name, err.message); }
  }; reader.readAsText(file);
}

function handleExtUpload(e) {
  const file = e.target.files[0]; if (!file) return;
  const reader = new FileReader();
  reader.onload = function(ev) {
    try {
      const { headers, rows } = parseCSV(ev.target.result); STATE.extWtgs = []; let count = 0;
      for (let i = 0; i < rows.length; i++) {
        const row = rows[i], vals = Object.values(row);
        const id = findColVal(headers, vals, ['id', 'name', 'wtg']);
        const x = parseFloat(findColVal(headers, vals, ['lat', 'latitude', 'x', 'easting']));
        const y = parseFloat(findColVal(headers, vals, ['lon', 'longitude', 'y', 'northing']));
        const rd = parseFloat(findColVal(headers, vals, ['rd', 'rotordiameter', 'rotor', 'diameter']));
        const hh = parseFloat(findColVal(headers, vals, ['hh', 'hubheight', 'hub']));
        if (!isNaN(x) && !isNaN(y)) { STATE.extWtgs.push({ id: id || `E${count + 1}`, name: id || `EXT-${count + 1}`, lat: x, lon: y, rd: rd || 100, hh: hh || 90 }); count++; }
      }
      setUploadStatus('extUploadZone', 'extUploadInfo', 'loaded', file.name, `${count} external WTGs`);
      renderExtTable();
    } catch (err) { setUploadStatus('extUploadZone', 'extUploadInfo', 'error', file.name, err.message); }
  }; reader.readAsText(file);
}

function handleMapUpload(e) {
  const file = e.target.files[0]; if (!file) return;
  const reader = new FileReader();
  reader.onload = function(ev) {
    try {
      const text = ev.target.result; STATE.terrainPoints = [];
      const lines = text.trim().split(/\r?\n/);
      for (const line of lines) {
        const trimmed = line.trim();
        if (!trimmed || trimmed.startsWith('"IG') || trimmed.startsWith('"DS') || trimmed.startsWith('"DP') || trimmed.startsWith('"TX') || trimmed.startsWith('"CS') || trimmed.startsWith('"NC')) continue;
        const parts = trimmed.replace(/^["']|["']$/g, '').split(/[\s,;\t]+/);
        if (parts.length >= 3) {
          const x = parseFloat(parts[0]), y = parseFloat(parts[1]), z = parseFloat(parts[2]);
          if (!isNaN(x) && !isNaN(y) && !isNaN(z)) STATE.terrainPoints.push({ x, y, z });
        }
      }
      STATE.hasMapData = STATE.terrainPoints.length > 50;
      const hasElev = STATE.terrainPoints.some(p => p.z !== 0);
      setUploadStatus('mapUploadZone', 'mapUploadInfo', 'loaded', file.name, `${STATE.terrainPoints.length.toLocaleString()} points${hasElev ? ' (with elevation)' : ' (coords only — synthetic terrain used)'}`);
    } catch (err) { setUploadStatus('mapUploadZone', 'mapUploadInfo', 'error', file.name, err.message); }
  }; reader.readAsText(file);
}

function addManualWTG() {
  const id = document.getElementById('wId').value || `W${STATE.wtgs.length + 1}`;
  const x = parseFloat(document.getElementById('wX').value), y = parseFloat(document.getElementById('wY').value);
  const rd = parseFloat(document.getElementById('wRD').value), hh = parseFloat(document.getElementById('wHH').value);
  if (isNaN(x) || isNaN(y) || isNaN(rd) || isNaN(hh)) { alert('Enter valid values'); return; }
  STATE.wtgs.push({ id, name: id, lat: x, lon: y, rd, hh });
  ['wId', 'wX', 'wY', 'wRD', 'wHH'].forEach(f => document.getElementById(f).value = '');
  renderWTGTable(); calcCentroid(); checkStep1Ready();
}

function renderWTGTable() {
  let h = '<table class="data-table"><thead><tr><th>ID</th><th>X/Lat</th><th>Y/Lon</th><th>RD (m)</th><th>HH (m)</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody>';
  for (let i = 0; i < STATE.wtgs.length; i++) { const w = STATE.wtgs[i]; h += `<tr><td><strong>${w.name}</strong></td><td>${w.lat}</td><td>${w.lon}</td><td>${w.rd}</td><td>${w.hh}</td><td><button class="btn btn-danger btn-sm" onclick="STATE.wtgs.splice(${i},1);renderWTGTable();calcCentroid();checkStep1Ready()">✕</button></td></tr>`; }
  h += '</tbody></table>'; document.getElementById('wtgTableWrap').innerHTML = h;
}

function renderExtTable() {
  let h = '<table class="data-table"><thead><tr><th>ID</th><th>X/Lat</th><th>Y/Lon</th><th>RD</th><th>HH</th></tr></thead><tbody>';
  for (const w of STATE.extWtgs) { h += `<tr><td>${w.name}</td><td>${w.lat}</td><td>${w.lon}</td><td>${w.rd}</td><td>${w.hh}</td></tr>`; }
  h += '</tbody></table>'; document.getElementById('extTableWrap').innerHTML = h;
}

function calcCentroid() {
  if (STATE.wtgs.length === 0) { STATE.layoutCentroid = null; return; }
  const avgX = STATE.wtgs.reduce((s, w) => s + w.lat, 0) / STATE.wtgs.length;
  const avgY = STATE.wtgs.reduce((s, w) => s + w.lon, 0) / STATE.wtgs.length;
  STATE.layoutCentroid = { lat: avgX, lon: avgY };
}

function checkStep1Ready() {
  document.getElementById('step1Next').disabled = STATE.wtgs.length === 0;
  if (STATE.wtgs.length > 0) markStepDone(1);
}

function loadDemoLayout() {
  STATE.wtgs = [
    { id: 'T1', name: 'T1', lat: 594263, lon: 4892488, rd: 163, hh: 138 },
    { id: 'T2', name: 'T2', lat: 594973, lon: 4892211, rd: 163, hh: 138 },
    { id: 'T3', name: 'T3', lat: 595683, lon: 4891934, rd: 163, hh: 138 },
    { id: 'T4', name: 'T4', lat: 589592, lon: 4888542, rd: 163, hh: 138 },
    { id: 'T5', name: 'T5', lat: 595825, lon: 4891207, rd: 163, hh: 138 },
    { id: 'T6', name: 'T6', lat: 593553, lon: 4892765, rd: 163, hh: 138 },
    { id: 'T7', name: 'T7', lat: 594155, lon: 4893000, rd: 163, hh: 138 },
    { id: 'T8', name: 'T8', lat: 595300, lon: 4891700, rd: 163, hh: 138 }
  ];
  STATE.extWtgs = [
    { id: '56', name: 'EXT-56', lat: 582376, lon: 4897793, rd: 90, hh: 90 },
    { id: '57', name: 'EXT-57', lat: 582261, lon: 4896654, rd: 90, hh: 90 },
    { id: '58', name: 'EXT-58', lat: 583396, lon: 4896865, rd: 90, hh: 90 },
    { id: '59', name: 'EXT-59', lat: 582571, lon: 4896282, rd: 90, hh: 90 }
  ];
  renderWTGTable(); renderExtTable(); calcCentroid(); checkStep1Ready();
}

function clearAll() {
  STATE.wtgs = []; STATE.extWtgs = []; STATE.terrainPoints = []; STATE.windData = []; STATE.windRoseData = null; STATE.proposedMasts = []; STATE.analysisResults = null; STATE.hasMapData = false; STATE.layoutCentroid = null;
  renderWTGTable(); renderExtTable(); checkStep1Ready();
  ['wtgUploadZone', 'extUploadZone', 'mapUploadZone', 'windUploadZone'].forEach(z => document.getElementById(z).classList.remove('loaded', 'error'));
  ['wtgUploadInfo', 'extUploadInfo', 'mapUploadInfo', 'windUploadInfo'].forEach(i => document.getElementById(i).style.display = 'none');
}

// ── STEP 2: WIND DATA ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
function autoFillERA5() {
  if (!STATE.layoutCentroid) return;
  const { lat, lon } = STATE.layoutCentroid;
  if (isGeo(lat, lon)) {
    document.getElementById('era5Lat').value = lat.toFixed(4);
    document.getElementById('era5Lon').value = lon.toFixed(4);
    document.getElementById('era5CoordNote').style.display = 'none';
  } else {
    document.getElementById('era5CoordNote').style.display = 'block';
  }
}

function handleWindUpload(e) {
  const file = e.target.files[0]; if (!file) return;
  const reader = new FileReader();
  reader.onload = function(ev) {
    try {
      const { headers, rows } = parseCSV(ev.target.result);
      const speedIdx = headers.findIndex(h => /speed|windspeed|ws/.test(h));
      const dirIdx = headers.findIndex(h => /dir|direction|winddir|wd/.test(h));
      if (speedIdx < 0 || dirIdx < 0) throw new Error('Cannot find speed/direction columns');
      STATE.windData = [];
      for (const row of rows) {
        const speed = parseFloat(Object.values(row)[speedIdx]), dir = parseFloat(Object.values(row)[dirIdx]);
        if (!isNaN(speed) && !isNaN(dir) && speed >= 0 && dir >= 0 && dir < 360) STATE.windData.push({ speed, direction: dir, timestamp: Object.values(row)[0] || '' });
      }
      if (STATE.windData.length === 0) throw new Error('No valid records');
      setUploadStatus('windUploadZone', 'windUploadInfo', 'loaded', file.name, `${STATE.windData.length.toLocaleString()} records`);
      computeWindRose(); markStepDone(2);
    } catch (err) { setUploadStatus('windUploadZone', 'windUploadInfo', 'error', file.name, err.message); }
  }; reader.readAsText(file);
}

async function downloadERA5() {
  const lat = parseFloat(document.getElementById('era5Lat').value), lon = parseFloat(document.getElementById('era5Lon').value), year = document.getElementById('era5Year').value;
  if (isNaN(lat) || isNaN(lon)) { alert('Enter valid coordinates'); return; }
  const statusEl = document.getElementById('era5Status');
  statusEl.innerHTML = '<div class="loading-spinner" style="width:20px;height:20px;display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle"></div> <span style="color:var(--mint);font-size:.75rem">Downloading ERA5T...</span>';
  try {
    const url = `https://archive-api.open-meteo.com/v1/archive?latitude=${lat}&longitude=${lon}&start_date=${year}-01-01&end_date=${year}-12-31&hourly=wind_speed_100m,wind_direction_100m&wind_speed_unit=ms&timezone=auto`;
    const resp = await fetch(url); if (!resp.ok) throw new Error(`HTTP ${resp.status}`);
    const data = await resp.json();
    if (!data.hourly || !data.hourly.wind_speed_100m) throw new Error('Invalid response');
    STATE.windData = [];
    for (let i = 0; i < data.hourly.wind_speed_100m.length; i++) {
      if (data.hourly.wind_speed_100m[i] !== null && data.hourly.wind_direction_100m[i] !== null)
        STATE.windData.push({ speed: data.hourly.wind_speed_100m[i], direction: data.hourly.wind_direction_100m[i], timestamp: data.hourly.time[i] || '' });
    }
    if (STATE.windData.length === 0) throw new Error('No valid data');
    setUploadStatus('windUploadZone', 'windUploadInfo', 'loaded', `ERA5T ${year}`, `${STATE.windData.length.toLocaleString()} records`);
    statusEl.innerHTML = `<div class="alert alert-success" style="margin:0">Downloaded ${STATE.windData.length.toLocaleString()} hourly records for ${lat.toFixed(3)}, ${lon.toFixed(3)} (${year})</div>`;
    computeWindRose(); markStepDone(2);
  } catch (err) { statusEl.innerHTML = `<div class="alert alert-error" style="margin:0">Download failed: ${err.message}</div>`; }
}

async function skipWindData() {
  if (STATE.windData.length > 0) { goToStep(3); return; }
  if (!STATE.layoutCentroid) { alert('Load WTG layout first.'); return; }
  const { lat, lon } = STATE.layoutCentroid;
  if (!isGeo(lat, lon)) { alert('Layout uses UTM coordinates. Please download ERA5 manually with geographic coordinates in Step 2.'); return; }
  document.getElementById('era5Lat').value = lat.toFixed(4);
  document.getElementById('era5Lon').value = lon.toFixed(4);
  await downloadERA5();
  if (STATE.windData.length > 0) goToStep(3);
}

function loadDemoWindData() {
  const data = [], predDir = 220;
  for (let d = 0; d < 365; d++) for (let h = 0; h < 24; h++) {
    const u = Math.random(), speed = 8.5 * Math.pow(-Math.log(1 - u), 1 / 2.1);
    const r = Math.random(); let direction;
    if (r < 0.35) direction = predDir + (Math.random() - 0.5) * 40;
    else if (r < 0.55) direction = 180 + (Math.random() - 0.5) * 30;
    else if (r < 0.70) direction = 270 + (Math.random() - 0.5) * 40;
    else direction = Math.random() * 360;
    direction = ((direction % 360) + 360) % 360;
    data.push({ speed: Math.round(speed * 100) / 100, direction: Math.round(direction * 10) / 10, timestamp: `2023-${String(Math.floor(d / 30) + 1).padStart(2, '0')}-${String((d % 30) + 1).padStart(2, '0')} ${String(h).padStart(2, '0')}:00` });
  }
  STATE.windData = data;
  setUploadStatus('windUploadZone', 'windUploadInfo', 'loaded', 'Demo Wind Data', `${data.length.toLocaleString()} records`);
  computeWindRose(); markStepDone(2);
}

// ── STEP 3: WIND ROSE ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
function computeWindRose() {
  if (STATE.windData.length === 0) return;
  const numSectors = 36, sectorWidth = 10, speedBins = [0, 3, 6, 9, 12, 15, 18, 21, 25, 30];
  const speedColors = ['#4a90d9', '#2d9cce', '#1db87e', '#7bc67e', '#f0a500', '#e87d20', '#e74c3c', '#c0392b', '#8b0000'];
  const sectors = []; let totalSpeed = 0, maxSpeed = 0, calmCount = 0;
  for (let i = 0; i < numSectors; i++) sectors.push({ dir: i * sectorWidth + sectorWidth / 2, dirStart: i * sectorWidth, dirEnd: (i + 1) * sectorWidth, count: 0, speedSum: 0, speedBins: new Array(speedBins.length - 1).fill(0) });
  for (const d of STATE.windData) { if (d.speed < 0.5) { calmCount++; continue; } totalSpeed += d.speed; if (d.speed > maxSpeed) maxSpeed = d.speed; const si = Math.floor(d.direction / sectorWidth) % numSectors; sectors[si].count++; sectors[si].speedSum += d.speed; const bi = speedBins.findIndex(b => d.speed < b) - 1; if (bi >= 0 && bi < speedBins.length - 1) sectors[si].speedBins[bi]++; }
  const total = STATE.windData.length - calmCount;
  const frequencies = sectors.map(s => total > 0 ? s.count / total : 0);
  const meanSpeed = total > 0 ? totalSpeed / total : 0;
  let predIdx = 0; for (let i = 1; i < numSectors; i++) if (sectors[i].count > sectors[predIdx].count) predIdx = i;
  const meanV = meanSpeed; const variance = STATE.windData.reduce((s, d) => s + (d.speed - meanV) ** 2, 0) / STATE.windData.length; const kWeibull = Math.pow(Math.sqrt(Math.max(variance, 0.001)) / meanV, -1.086);
  STATE.windRoseData = { sectors, frequencies, numSectors, sectorWidth, speedBins, speedColors, predominant: { direction: sectors[predIdx].dir, frequency: total > 0 ? (sectors[predIdx].count / total * 100) : 0, count: sectors[predIdx].count }, meanSpeed: Math.round(meanSpeed * 100) / 100, maxSpeed: Math.round(maxSpeed * 100) / 100, calmHours: calmCount, calmPct: STATE.windData.length > 0 ? (calmCount / STATE.windData.length * 100) : 0, totalRecords: STATE.windData.length, weibullK: Math.round(kWeibull * 100) / 100 };
  document.getElementById('step3Next').disabled = false; markStepDone(3);
}

function renderWindRose() {
  if (STATE.windData.length === 0) { document.getElementById('noWindAlert').style.display = 'block'; document.getElementById('windRoseSection').style.display = 'none'; return; }
  document.getElementById('noWindAlert').style.display = 'none'; document.getElementById('windRoseSection').style.display = 'block';
  if (!STATE.windRoseData) computeWindRose(); if (!STATE.windRoseData) return;
  const wr = STATE.windRoseData;
  document.getElementById('predDirValue').textContent = `${wr.predominant.direction}° (${degToCompass(wr.predominant.direction)})`;
  document.getElementById('statMeanSpeed').textContent = wr.meanSpeed.toFixed(1);
  document.getElementById('statMaxSpeed').textContent = wr.maxSpeed.toFixed(1);
  document.getElementById('statPredFreq').textContent = wr.predominant.frequency.toFixed(1) + '%';
  document.getElementById('statCalmHours').textContent = wr.calmHours.toLocaleString();
  document.getElementById('statRecords').textContent = wr.totalRecords.toLocaleString();
  document.getElementById('statWeibullK').textContent = wr.weibullK.toFixed(2);
  drawWindRose('windRoseCanvas', wr);
  let html = '<table class="data-table"><thead><tr><th>Dir (°)</th><th>Compass</th><th>Count</th><th>Freq (%)</th><th>Mean Speed</th></tr></thead><tbody>';
  for (const s of wr.sectors) { const freq = STATE.windData.length > 0 ? (s.count / STATE.windData.length * 100) : 0; const avgSpd = s.count > 0 ? (s.speedSum / s.count) : 0; const isPred = Math.abs(s.dir - wr.predominant.direction) <= 15; html += `<tr style="${isPred ? 'background:rgba(29,184,126,.08)' : ''}"><td>${s.dirStart}°–${s.dirEnd}°</td><td>${degToCompass(s.dir)}</td><td>${s.count.toLocaleString()}</td><td>${freq.toFixed(1)}%</td><td>${avgSpd.toFixed(1)} m/s</td></tr>`; }
  html += '</tbody></table>'; document.getElementById('sectorTableWrap').innerHTML = html;
}

function drawWindRose(canvasId, wr) {
  const canvas = document.getElementById(canvasId); if (!canvas) return;
  const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d'), W = canvas.width, H = canvas.height, cx = W / 2, cy = H / 2, maxR = Math.min(W, H) / 2 - 50;
  ctx.clearRect(0, 0, W, H); ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(11,31,58,0.5)'; ctx.beginPath(); ctx.arc(cx, cy, maxR + 10, 0, Math.PI * 2); ctx.fill();
  const maxFreq = Math.max(...wr.frequencies, 0.01);
  for (let r = 1; r <= 4; r++) { const rad = maxR * r / 4; ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.08)'; ctx.lineWidth = 1; ctx.beginPath(); ctx.arc(cx, cy, rad, 0, Math.PI * 2); ctx.stroke(); ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.2)'; ctx.font = '9px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'center'; ctx.fillText((maxFreq * r / 4 * 100).toFixed(0) + '%', cx, cy - rad + 10); }
  const dirs = ['N', 'NE', 'E', 'SE', 'S', 'SW', 'W', 'NW'];
  for (let i = 0; i < 8; i++) { const ang = (i * 45 - 90) * Math.PI / 180; ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.5)'; ctx.font = 'bold 11px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'center'; ctx.textBaseline = 'middle'; ctx.fillText(dirs[i], cx + (maxR + 25) * Math.cos(ang), cy + (maxR + 25) * Math.sin(ang)); }
  const sectorAngle = (2 * Math.PI) / wr.numSectors;
  for (let i = 0; i < wr.numSectors; i++) {
    const startAng = (wr.sectors[i].dirStart - 90) * Math.PI / 180 - sectorAngle / 2, endAng = startAng + sectorAngle, s = wr.sectors[i], total = STATE.windData.length || 1;
    let currentR = 0;
    for (let b = 0; b < s.speedBins.length; b++) { const binFreq = s.speedBins[b] / total, binR = (binFreq / maxFreq) * maxR; if (binR < 0.3) { currentR += binR; continue; } ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(cx, cy); ctx.arc(cx, cy, currentR + binR, startAng, endAng); ctx.closePath(); ctx.fillStyle = wr.speedColors[b]; ctx.globalAlpha = 0.75; ctx.fill(); ctx.globalAlpha = 1; currentR += binR; }
    ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(cx, cy); ctx.arc(cx, cy, currentR, startAng, endAng); ctx.closePath(); ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(0,0,0,.3)'; ctx.lineWidth = 0.5; ctx.stroke();
  }
  const predAng = (wr.predominant.direction - 90) * Math.PI / 180, arrowLen = maxR * 0.9;
  ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(cx, cy); ctx.lineTo(cx + arrowLen * Math.cos(predAng), cy + arrowLen * Math.sin(predAng)); ctx.strokeStyle = '#f0a500'; ctx.lineWidth = 2.5; ctx.setLineDash([6, 4]); ctx.stroke(); ctx.setLineDash([]);
  ctx.beginPath(); ctx.arc(cx + arrowLen * Math.cos(predAng), cy + arrowLen * Math.sin(predAng), 5, 0, Math.PI * 2); ctx.fillStyle = '#f0a500'; ctx.fill();
  ctx.beginPath(); ctx.arc(cx, cy, 4, 0, Math.PI * 2); ctx.fillStyle = '#fff'; ctx.fill();
  const legendX = 10, legendY = H - 15; ctx.font = '9px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'left'; ctx.textBaseline = 'bottom';
  ['0-3', '3-6', '6-9', '9-12', '12-15', '15-18', '18-21', '21-25', '25+'].forEach((l, i) => { const lx = legendX + i * 50; ctx.fillStyle = wr.speedColors[i]; ctx.fillRect(lx, legendY - 8, 10, 8); ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.5)'; ctx.fillText(l + ' m/s', lx + 12, legendY); });
}

// ── STEP 4: LAYOUT VISUALIZATION ────────────────────────────────────────────
function renderLayout() {
  const canvas = document.getElementById('layoutCanvas'); const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');
  const allPoints = [...STATE.wtgs.map(w => ({ x: w.lat, y: w.lon })), ...STATE.extWtgs.map(w => ({ x: w.lat, y: w.lon })), ...STATE.proposedMasts.map(m => ({ x: m.lat, y: m.lon }))];
  if (allPoints.length === 0) return;
  const xs = allPoints.map(p => p.x), ys = allPoints.map(p => p.y);
  const minX = Math.min(...xs), maxX = Math.max(...xs), minY = Math.min(...ys), maxY = Math.max(...ys);
  const rangeX = maxX - minX || 1, rangeY = maxY - minY || 1, pad = 80;
  const scale = Math.min((canvas.width - pad * 2) / rangeX, (canvas.height - pad * 2) / rangeY);
  const offsetX = pad + ((canvas.width - pad * 2) - rangeX * scale) / 2, offsetY = pad + ((canvas.height - pad * 2) - rangeY * scale) / 2;
  function toScreen(x, y) { return { sx: offsetX + (x - minX) * scale, sy: offsetY + (maxY - y) * scale }; }
  ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(11,31,58,0.7)'; ctx.fillRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);
  ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.05)'; ctx.lineWidth = 1;
  const gridStep = Math.pow(10, Math.floor(Math.log10(Math.max(rangeX, rangeY) / 5)));
  for (let gx = Math.ceil(minX / gridStep) * gridStep; gx <= maxX; gx += gridStep) { const { sx } = toScreen(gx, 0); ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(sx, pad); ctx.lineTo(sx, canvas.height - pad); ctx.stroke(); }
  for (let gy = Math.ceil(minY / gridStep) * gridStep; gy <= maxY; gy += gridStep) { const { sy } = toScreen(0, gy); ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(pad, sy); ctx.lineTo(canvas.width - pad, sy); ctx.stroke(); }

  // First-row identification
  const predDir = STATE.windRoseData ? STATE.windRoseData.predominant.direction : 0;
  const firstRowIds = new Set();
  if (STATE.windRoseData) {
    for (const w of STATE.wtgs) { let isFR = true;
      for (const other of STATE.wtgs) { if (other.id === w.id) continue; const dist = getDist(w, other); const ang = getBearing(w, other); if (angularDev(ang, predDir) <= 15 && dist <= 20 * w.rd) { isFR = false; break; } }
      if (isFR) firstRowIds.add(w.id); }
  }

  // Proposed mast → target WTG lines
  for (const m of STATE.proposedMasts) { const ms = toScreen(m.lat, m.lon); const ws = toScreen(m.targetWTG.lat, m.targetWTG.lon); ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(ms.sx, ms.sy); ctx.lineTo(ws.sx, ws.sy); ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(240,165,0,.6)'; ctx.lineWidth = 2; ctx.setLineDash([6, 4]); ctx.stroke(); ctx.setLineDash([]); }

  // Predominant wind arrows
  if (STATE.windRoseData) { const ang = (predDir - 90) * Math.PI / 180;
    for (const w of STATE.wtgs) { const ws = toScreen(w.lat, w.lon); const arrLen = 45; ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(ws.sx, ws.sy); ctx.lineTo(ws.sx + arrLen * Math.cos(ang), ws.sy + arrLen * Math.sin(ang)); ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(240,165,0,.4)'; ctx.lineWidth = 1.5; ctx.stroke(); }
  }

  // External WTGs (gold diamonds)
  for (const w of STATE.extWtgs) { const { sx, sy } = toScreen(w.lat, w.lon); const s = 7; ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(sx, sy - s); ctx.lineTo(sx + s, sy); ctx.lineTo(sx, sy + s); ctx.lineTo(sx - s, sy); ctx.closePath(); ctx.fillStyle = '#f0a500'; ctx.fill(); ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.5)'; ctx.font = '9px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'center'; ctx.fillText(w.name, sx, sy + s + 12); }

  // WTGs (green=first-row, blue=others)
  for (const w of STATE.wtgs) { const { sx, sy } = toScreen(w.lat, w.lon); const isFR = firstRowIds.has(w.id); const r = 10; ctx.beginPath(); ctx.arc(sx, sy, r, 0, Math.PI * 2); ctx.fillStyle = isFR ? '#1db87e' : '#2d9cce'; ctx.fill(); ctx.strokeStyle = isFR ? 'rgba(29,184,126,.4)' : 'rgba(45,156,206,.4)'; ctx.lineWidth = 2; ctx.stroke(); ctx.fillStyle = '#fff'; ctx.font = 'bold 10px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'center'; ctx.fillText(w.name, sx, sy + r + 14); }

  // Proposed masts (red triangles)
  for (const m of STATE.proposedMasts) { const { sx, sy } = toScreen(m.lat, m.lon); const s = 12; ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(sx, sy - s * 1.3); ctx.lineTo(sx - s, sy + s * 0.7); ctx.lineTo(sx + s, sy + s * 0.7); ctx.closePath(); ctx.fillStyle = '#e74c3c'; ctx.fill(); ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(231,76,60,.4)'; ctx.lineWidth = 2; ctx.stroke(); ctx.fillStyle = '#fff'; ctx.font = 'bold 9px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'center'; ctx.fillText(m.name, sx, sy + s + 14); }

  // Compass
  const crX = canvas.width - 50, crY = 50, crR = 30;
  ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.3)'; ctx.lineWidth = 1; ctx.beginPath(); ctx.arc(crX, crY, crR, 0, Math.PI * 2); ctx.stroke();
  ['N', 'E', 'S', 'W'].forEach((d, i) => { const a = (i * 90 - 90) * Math.PI / 180; ctx.fillStyle = d === 'N' ? '#e74c3c' : 'rgba(255,255,255,.5)'; ctx.font = 'bold 10px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'center'; ctx.textBaseline = 'middle'; ctx.fillText(d, crX + (crR + 10) * Math.cos(a), crY + (crR + 10) * Math.sin(a)); });

  // Scale bar
  const scaleDist = gridStep, scalePx = scaleDist * scale, sbX = pad, sbY = canvas.height - 30;
  ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.5)'; ctx.lineWidth = 2; ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(sbX, sbY); ctx.lineTo(sbX + scalePx, sbY); ctx.stroke();
  ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(sbX, sbY - 4); ctx.lineTo(sbX, sbY + 4); ctx.stroke(); ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(sbX + scalePx, sbY - 4); ctx.lineTo(sbX + scalePx, sbY + 4); ctx.stroke();
  ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.5)'; ctx.font = '9px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'center'; ctx.fillText(`${scaleDist.toFixed(0)} m`, sbX + scalePx / 2, sbY - 6);

  // Legend
  const items = [
    { color: '#2d9cce', shape: 'circle', label: 'WTG' },
    { color: '#1db87e', shape: 'circle', label: 'First-Row WTG' },
    { color: '#f0a500', shape: 'diamond', label: 'External WTG' },
    { color: '#e74c3c', shape: 'tri', label: 'Proposed Mast' },
    { color: '#f0a500', shape: 'arrow', label: 'Pred. Wind FROM' }
  ];
  if (STATE.proposedMasts.length > 0) items.push({ color: '#f0a500', shape: 'dash', label: 'Mast–WTG Link' });
  let legHtml = '';
  for (const li of items) { legHtml += `<span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.3rem;font-size:.65rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5)">`; legHtml += `<span style="width:10px;height:10px;background:${li.color};border-radius:${li.shape === 'circle' ? '50%' : li.shape === 'diamond' ? '2px' : '0'};display:inline-block;${li.shape === 'diamond' ? 'transform:rotate(45deg)' : ''}"></span>${li.label}</span>`; }
  document.getElementById('layoutLegend').innerHTML = legHtml;
  document.getElementById('layoutMetrics').innerHTML = `
    <div class="metric-item"><span class="metric-val">${STATE.wtgs.length}</span><span class="metric-label">Target WTGs</span></div>
    <div class="metric-item"><span class="metric-val" style="color:var(--mint)">${firstRowIds.size}</span><span class="metric-label">First-Row WTGs</span></div>
    <div class="metric-item"><span class="metric-val">${STATE.extWtgs.length}</span><span class="metric-label">External WTGs</span></div>
    <div class="metric-item"><span class="metric-val">${STATE.proposedMasts.length}</span><span class="metric-label">Proposed Masts</span></div>`;
}

// ── STEP 5: MAST PROPOSAL ENGINE ────────────────────────────────────────────
function runFullAnalysis() {
  if (STATE.wtgs.length === 0) { alert('Load WTG layout first.'); return; }
  if (STATE.windData.length === 0) { alert('No wind data. Go to Step 2 to download ERA5T.'); return; }
  if (!STATE.windRoseData) computeWindRose();

  const prog = document.getElementById('analysisProgress'); prog.style.display = 'block';
  const bar = document.getElementById('analysisProgressBar'); bar.style.width = '10%';
  const statusTxt = document.getElementById('analysisStatusText');
  statusTxt.textContent = 'Identifying first-row WTGs...';
  document.getElementById('analysisAlerts').innerHTML = '';
  document.getElementById('analysisResults').style.display = 'none';

  setTimeout(() => {
    try {
      const config = {
        sectorWidth: parseInt(document.getElementById('cfgSector').value),
        assessmentRadius: parseFloat(document.getElementById('cfgRadius').value) || 5000,
        minDistanceD: parseFloat(document.getElementById('cfgMinDist').value) || 2,
        wakeAngularThreshold: parseFloat(document.getElementById('cfgWakeAng').value) || 30,
        wakeDistanceThresholdD: parseFloat(document.getElementById('cfgWakeDist').value) || 20,
        minFreeSector: parseFloat(document.getElementById('cfgMinFree').value) || 20
      };
      const predDir = STATE.windRoseData.predominant.direction;

      bar.style.width = '20%'; statusTxt.textContent = 'Calculating free measurement sectors...';

      // Identify first-row WTGs and free measurement sectors
      const firstRowWTGs = [];
      for (const w of STATE.wtgs) {
        let isFR = true; const blockingWTGs = [];
        for (const other of STATE.wtgs) { if (other.id === w.id) continue; const dist = getDist(w, other); const ang = getBearing(w, other); if (angularDev(ang, predDir) <= 15 && dist <= 20 * w.rd) { isFR = false; blockingWTGs.push(other.name); } }
        for (const ext of STATE.extWtgs) { const dist = getDist(w, ext); const ang = getBearing(w, ext); if (angularDev(ang, predDir) <= 15 && dist <= 20 * w.rd) { isFR = false; blockingWTGs.push(ext.name); } }
        const freeSectorSpan = calcFreeSector(w, [...STATE.wtgs, ...STATE.extWtgs], config);
        firstRowWTGs.push({ ...w, isFirstRow: isFR, blockingWTGs, freeSectorSpan });
      }

      bar.style.width = '40%'; statusTxt.textContent = 'Generating candidate mast positions...';

      // Filter qualifying WTGs: prefer first-row with >=20° free sector
      let qualifying = firstRowWTGs.filter(w => w.isFirstRow && w.freeSectorSpan >= config.minFreeSector);
      if (qualifying.length === 0) { qualifying = firstRowWTGs.filter(w => w.isFirstRow); }
      if (qualifying.length === 0) { qualifying = [...firstRowWTGs].sort((a, b) => b.freeSectorSpan - a.freeSectorSpan).slice(0, 3); }

      // Generate candidate mast positions
      const candidates = [];
      const distances = [2, 2.5, 3, 3.5, 4, 5];
      const offsets = [0, -5, -10, 5, 10];
      for (const wtg of qualifying) {
        for (const distD of distances) {
          const actualDist = distD * wtg.rd;
          for (const offset of offsets) {
            const bearing = predDir + offset; // Mast placed UPWIND (in direction wind comes FROM)
            let mLat, mLon;
            if (isGeo(wtg.lat, wtg.lon)) { const pt = destPoint(wtg.lat, wtg.lon, bearing, actualDist); mLat = pt.lat; mLon = pt.lon; }
            else { mLat = wtg.lat + actualDist * Math.sin(bearing * Math.PI / 180); mLon = wtg.lon + actualDist * Math.cos(bearing * Math.PI / 180); }
            candidates.push({ name: `Mast-${candidates.length + 1}`, lat: mLat, lon: mLon, height: wtg.hh, targetWTG: wtg, distance: actualDist, distanceD: distD, bearingFromWTG: bearing, offset });
          }
        }
      }

      bar.style.width = '60%'; statusTxt.textContent = `Evaluating ${candidates.length} candidate positions...`;

      // Evaluate each candidate
      const scored = [];
      for (let i = 0; i < candidates.length; i++) {
        const c = candidates[i];
        const mast = { id: c.name, name: c.name, lat: c.lat, lon: c.lon, height: c.height };
        const assessment = performTerrainAssessment(mast, c.targetWTG, STATE.wtgs, STATE.extWtgs, STATE.terrainPoints, config);

        // Check secondary WTGs (for 1-mast-2-WTG)
        const secondaries = [];
        for (const wtg of STATE.wtgs) {
          if (wtg.id === c.targetWTG.id) continue;
          const a2 = performTerrainAssessment(mast, wtg, STATE.wtgs, STATE.extWtgs, STATE.terrainPoints, config);
          if (a2.isCompliant && a2.distanceD >= config.minDistanceD) secondaries.push({ wtg, assessment: a2, score: scoreAssessment(a2) });
        }
        secondaries.sort((a, b) => b.score - a.score);

        const score = scoreCandidate(c, assessment, secondaries);
        scored.push({ ...c, assessment, secondaries, score, numServeable: 1 + Math.min(secondaries.length, 2) });

        if (i % 10 === 0) { bar.style.width = `${60 + (i / candidates.length) * 30}%`; }
      }

      bar.style.width = '90%'; statusTxt.textContent = 'Selecting optimal mast locations...';

      scored.sort((a, b) => b.score - a.score);

      // Deduplicate (remove candidates within 1.5D of each other)
      const selected = [];
      for (const c of scored) {
        let tooClose = false;
        for (const sel of selected) { if (getDist(c, sel) < Math.min(c.targetWTG.rd, sel.targetWTG.rd) * 1.5) { tooClose = true; break; } }
        if (!tooClose) selected.push(c);
        if (selected.length >= 5) break;
      }

      // Form configurations
      const configs = [];
      for (const m of selected) {
        if (m.secondaries.length > 0) configs.push({ mast: m, primary: m.targetWTG, secondary: m.secondaries[0].wtg, secScore: m.secondaries[0].score, score: m.score });
        else configs.push({ mast: m, primary: m.targetWTG, secondary: null, secScore: 0, score: m.score });
      }

      // Recommendations
      const recs = [];
      const frCount = firstRowWTGs.filter(w => w.isFirstRow).length;
      recs.push(`${frCount} of ${STATE.wtgs.length} WTGs identified as first-row turbines facing the predominant wind direction (${predDir}°).`);
      const qualifyingCount = qualifying.filter(w => w.isFirstRow && w.freeSectorSpan >= config.minFreeSector).length;
      recs.push(`${qualifyingCount} WTGs meet both first-row and minimum ${config.minFreeSector}° free sector criteria.`);
      if (selected.length > 0) {
        const best = selected[0]; recs.push(`<strong>Recommended Primary Mast Location:</strong> ${best.name} at (${best.lat.toFixed(1)}, ${best.lon.toFixed(1)}), targeting ${best.targetWTG.name} at ${best.distanceD.toFixed(1)}D. Score: ${best.score}/100.`);
        if (selected[0].secondaries.length > 0) recs.push(`This mast can also serve ${selected[0].secondaries[0].wtg.name} (secondary WTG), enabling a 1-mast-2-WTGs PCV configuration.`);
      }
      if (frCount === 0) recs.push('No first-row WTGs found. All turbines have upstream wake effects. Consider the layout and predominant wind direction carefully.');
      if (selected.length > 0 && selected[0].score < 50) recs.push('Best candidate score is below 50. Consider relaxing criteria or reviewing the layout.');
      if (configs.filter(c => c.secondary).length > 0) recs.push(`${configs.filter(c => c.secondary).length} mast location(s) can serve 2 WTGs simultaneously, reducing measurement campaign cost.`);

      STATE.proposedMasts = selected;
      STATE.analysisResults = { config, predDir, firstRowWTGs, candidates: scored.slice(0, 30), proposedMasts: selected, configs, recommendations: recs };

      bar.style.width = '100%'; statusTxt.textContent = 'Analysis complete!';
      setTimeout(() => { prog.style.display = 'none'; }, 1000);

      renderProposalResults();
      document.getElementById('analysisResults').style.display = 'block';
      document.getElementById('step5Next').disabled = false;
      markStepDone(4); markStepDone(5);
    } catch (err) { prog.style.display = 'none'; document.getElementById('analysisAlerts').innerHTML = `<div class="alert alert-error">Analysis error: ${err.message}</div>`; }
  }, 100);
}

function calcFreeSector(wtg, allWtgs, config) {
  const numSectors = 360 / config.sectorWidth;
  let maxFree = 0, curFree = 0;
  for (let i = 0; i < numSectors; i++) {
    const dir = i * config.sectorWidth;
    let blocked = false;
    for (const other of allWtgs) {
      if (other.id === wtg.id) continue;
      const dist = getDist(wtg, other), ang = getBearing(wtg, other);
      if (angularDev(ang, dir) <= 15 && dist <= 20 * (wtg.rd || 100)) { blocked = true; break; }
    }
    if (!blocked) { curFree += config.sectorWidth; maxFree = Math.max(maxFree, curFree); } else { curFree = 0; }
  }
  return maxFree;
}

function scoreAssessment(a) {
  let distScore = 100;
  if (a.distanceD < 2) distScore = a.distanceD / 2 * 50;
  else if (a.distanceD > 6) distScore = Math.max(0, 80 - (a.distanceD - 6) * 10);
  return (distScore * 0.3 + a.validPct * 0.4 + (a.freestreamCount / a.numSectors) * 100 * 0.3);
}

function scoreCandidate(c, assessment, secondaries) {
  let distScore = 100;
  if (c.distanceD < 2) distScore = c.distanceD / 2 * 50;
  else if (c.distanceD > 6) distScore = Math.max(0, 80 - (c.distanceD - 6) * 10);
  const terrainScore = assessment.validPct;
  const freeScore = (assessment.freestreamCount / assessment.numSectors) * 100;
  const frBonus = c.targetWTG.isFirstRow ? 15 : 0;
  const freeSpan = c.targetWTG.freeSectorSpan || 0;
  const freeSpanBonus = freeSpan >= 40 ? 10 : freeSpan >= 20 ? 5 : 0;
  const multiBonus = secondaries.length > 0 ? Math.min(15, 5 + secondaries[0].score / 20) : 0;
  const offsetPenalty = Math.abs(c.offset) * 0.3;
  return Math.round(Math.min(100, Math.max(0, distScore * 0.25 + terrainScore * 0.25 + freeScore * 0.2 + frBonus + freeSpanBonus + multiBonus - offsetPenalty)) * 10) / 10;
}

function renderProposalResults() {
  const r = STATE.analysisResults; if (!r) return;
  const frCount = r.firstRowWTGs.filter(w => w.isFirstRow).length;
  const bestScore = r.proposedMasts.length > 0 ? r.proposedMasts[0].score : 0;
  const avgFree = r.firstRowWTGs.length > 0 ? Math.round(r.firstRowWTGs.reduce((s, w) => s + w.freeSectorSpan, 0) / r.firstRowWTGs.length) : 0;
  const multiConfigs = r.configs.filter(c => c.secondary).length;

  document.getElementById('proposalMetrics').innerHTML = `
    <div class="metric-item"><span class="metric-val">${r.proposedMasts.length}</span><span class="metric-label">Proposed Mast Sites</span></div>
    <div class="metric-item"><span class="metric-val">${frCount}</span><span class="metric-label">First-Row WTGs</span></div>
    <div class="metric-item"><span class="metric-val">${bestScore}</span><span class="metric-label">Best Score</span></div>
    <div class="metric-item"><span class="metric-val">${multiConfigs}</span><span class="metric-label">2-WTG Configs</span></div>`;

  // First-row table
  let html = '<table class="data-table"><thead><tr><th>WTG</th><th>First Row</th><th>Free Sector</th><th>Blocking</th><th>Qualifies</th></tr></thead><tbody>';
  const minFree = parseFloat(document.getElementById('cfgMinFree').value) || 20;
  for (const w of r.firstRowWTGs) { const qualifies = w.isFirstRow && w.freeSectorSpan >= minFree; html += `<tr><td><strong>${w.name}</strong></td><td>${w.isFirstRow ? '<span class="badge badge-first">YES</span>' : '<span class="badge badge-warn">NO</span>'}</td><td>${w.freeSectorSpan}°</td><td>${w.blockingWTGs.length > 0 ? w.blockingWTGs.join(', ') : '<span style="color:var(--mint)">—</span>'}</td><td>${qualifies ? '<span class="badge badge-valid">YES</span>' : '<span class="badge badge-invalid">NO</span>'}</td></tr>`; }
  html += '</tbody></table>'; document.getElementById('firstRowTable').innerHTML = html;

  // Proposed masts table
  html = '<table class="data-table"><thead><tr><th>#</th><th>Proposed Mast</th><th>Coordinates</th><th>Target WTG</th><th>Dist (D)</th><th>Valid Sec.</th><th>Terrain</th><th>Serve</th><th>Score</th></tr></thead><tbody>';
  r.proposedMasts.forEach((m, i) => {
    const scoreClass = m.score >= 70 ? 'color:var(--mint)' : m.score >= 50 ? 'color:var(--sky4)' : m.score >= 30 ? 'color:var(--gold)' : 'color:#e74c3c';
    html += `<tr><td>${i + 1}</td><td><strong>${m.name}</strong></td><td>${m.lat.toFixed(0)}, ${m.lon.toFixed(0)}</td><td>${m.targetWTG.name}</td><td>${m.distanceD.toFixed(1)}</td><td>${m.assessment.validCount}/${m.assessment.numSectors}</td><td><span class="badge ${m.assessment.terrainClass === 'A' ? 'badge-valid' : m.assessment.terrainClass === 'B' ? 'badge-warn' : 'badge-invalid'}">${m.assessment.terrainClass}</span></td><td>${m.numServeable} WTG${m.numServeable > 1 ? 's' : ''}</td><td><strong style="${scoreClass}">${m.score}</strong></td></tr>`;
  });
  html += '</tbody></table>'; document.getElementById('mastProposalTable').innerHTML = html;

  // Config table
  html = '<table class="data-table"><thead><tr><th>Mast Location</th><th>Primary WTG</th><th>Secondary WTG</th><th>Score</th></tr></thead><tbody>';
  for (const c of r.configs) { html += `<tr><td><strong>${c.mast.name}</strong></td><td>${c.primary.name}</td><td>${c.secondary ? c.secondary.name + ' (' + c.secScore.toFixed(0) + ')' : '<span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.3)">—</span>'}</td><td><strong style="color:var(--mint)">${c.score}</strong></td></tr>`; }
  html += '</tbody></table>'; document.getElementById('configTable').innerHTML = html;

  // Recommendations
  let recHtml = '';
  for (const rec of r.recommendations) { const type = rec.includes('⚠') || rec.includes('No first-row') || rec.includes('below 50') ? 'warning' : 'success'; recHtml += `<div class="alert alert-${type}">${rec}</div>`; }
  document.getElementById('recommendations').innerHTML = recHtml;
}

// ── STEP 6: DETAILED REPORT ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
function switchReportTab(tabName) {
  if (!STATE.analysisResults) { document.getElementById('noAnalysisAlert').style.display = 'block'; document.getElementById('reportSection').style.display = 'none'; return; }
  document.getElementById('noAnalysisAlert').style.display = 'none'; document.getElementById('reportSection').style.display = 'block';
  document.querySelectorAll('#reportTabs .tab').forEach(t => t.classList.remove('active')); document.querySelectorAll('#reportSection .tab-panel').forEach(p => p.classList.remove('active'));
  if (event && event.target) event.target.classList.add('active'); else document.querySelector('#reportTabs .tab').classList.add('active');
  document.getElementById('tab-' + tabName).classList.add('active');
  if (tabName === 'terrain') { populateTerrainSelect(); }
  if (tabName === 'freestream') renderFreestream();
}

function populateTerrainSelect() {
  if (!STATE.analysisResults) return;
  const sel = document.getElementById('terrainPairSelect'); sel.innerHTML = '';
  for (const m of STATE.analysisResults.proposedMasts) {
    const opt = document.createElement('option'); opt.value = m.name; opt.textContent = `${m.name} → ${m.targetWTG.name} (Score: ${m.score})`; sel.appendChild(opt);
    if (m.secondaries.length > 0) { const opt2 = document.createElement('option'); opt2.value = m.name + '_sec'; opt2.textContent = `${m.name} → ${m.secondaries[0].wtg.name} (Secondary)`; sel.appendChild(opt2); }
  }
  renderTerrainDetail();
}

function renderTerrainDetail() {
  if (!STATE.analysisResults) return;
  const selKey = document.getElementById('terrainPairSelect').value;
  let mast, wtg;
  if (selKey.includes('_sec')) { const baseName = selKey.replace('_sec', ''); const m = STATE.analysisResults.proposedMasts.find(p => p.name === baseName); if (!m || !m.secondaries[0]) return; mast = { id: m.name, name: m.name, lat: m.lat, lon: m.lon, height: m.height }; wtg = m.secondaries[0].wtg; }
  else { const m = STATE.analysisResults.proposedMasts.find(p => p.name === selKey); if (!m) return; mast = { id: m.name, name: m.name, lat: m.lat, lon: m.lon, height: m.height }; wtg = m.targetWTG; }
  const config = STATE.analysisResults.config;
  const assessment = performTerrainAssessment(mast, wtg, STATE.wtgs, STATE.extWtgs, STATE.terrainPoints, config);

  drawTerrainPolar('terrainPolarCanvas', assessment);

  // Profile direction selector
  const dirSel = document.getElementById('profileDirSelect'); dirSel.innerHTML = '';
  for (const s of assessment.sectors) { dirSel.innerHTML += `<option value="${s.dir}">${s.dir}° ${s.isFreestream ? '(Freestream)' : ''} ${!s.isValid ? '(Invalid)' : ''}</option>`; }

  // Sector table
  let html = '<table class="data-table"><thead><tr><th>Dir°</th><th>Class</th><th>Max Slope</th><th>Freestream</th><th>Valid</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead><tbody>';
  for (const s of assessment.sectors) { const cc = s.terrainClass === 'A' ? 'badge-valid' : s.terrainClass === 'B' ? 'badge-warn' : 'badge-invalid'; html += `<tr><td>${s.dir}°</td><td><span class="badge ${cc}">Class ${s.terrainClass}</span></td><td>${s.maxSlopeDeg.toFixed(1)}°</td><td>${s.isFreestream ? '✅' : '❌'}</td><td>${s.isValid ? '✅' : '❌'}</td><td style="font-size:.65rem">${s.failures.length > 0 ? s.failures[0] : 'OK'}</td></tr>`; }
  html += '</tbody></table>'; document.getElementById('terrainSectorTable').innerHTML = html;

  // Terrain profile
  const selDir = parseInt(dirSel.value); const selSector = assessment.sectors.find(s => s.dir === selDir) || assessment.sectors[0];
  drawTerrainProfile('terrainProfileCanvas', selSector);
}

function drawTerrainPolar(canvasId, assessment) {
  const canvas = document.getElementById(canvasId); if (!canvas) return;
  const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d'), W = canvas.width, H = canvas.height, cx = W / 2, cy = H / 2, maxR = Math.min(W, H) / 2 - 50;
  ctx.clearRect(0, 0, W, H); ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(11,31,58,0.5)'; ctx.beginPath(); ctx.arc(cx, cy, maxR + 10, 0, Math.PI * 2); ctx.fill();
  for (let r = 1; r <= 4; r++) { ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.06)'; ctx.beginPath(); ctx.arc(cx, cy, maxR * r / 4, 0, Math.PI * 2); ctx.stroke(); }
  ['N', 'NE', 'E', 'SE', 'S', 'SW', 'W', 'NW'].forEach((d, i) => { const ang = (i * 45 - 90) * Math.PI / 180; ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.4)'; ctx.font = '10px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'center'; ctx.textBaseline = 'middle'; ctx.fillText(d, cx + (maxR + 22) * Math.cos(ang), cy + (maxR + 22) * Math.sin(ang)); });
  const sectorAng = (2 * Math.PI) / assessment.numSectors;
  for (const s of assessment.sectors) {
    const sAng = (s.dir - 90) * Math.PI / 180 - sectorAng / 2, eAng = sAng + sectorAng;
    let color = (!s.isValid && !s.isFreestream) ? 'rgba(231,76,60,.4)' : (!s.isValid || !s.isFreestream) ? 'rgba(240,165,0,.5)' : 'rgba(29,184,126,.6)';
    const slopeNorm = Math.min(s.maxSlopeDeg / 15, 1), r = maxR * (0.3 + slopeNorm * 0.7);
    ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(cx, cy); ctx.arc(cx, cy, r, sAng, eAng); ctx.closePath(); ctx.fillStyle = color; ctx.fill(); ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(0,0,0,.3)'; ctx.lineWidth = 0.5; ctx.stroke();
  }
  // Predominant wind arrow
  if (STATE.analysisResults) { const predAng = (STATE.analysisResults.predDir - 90) * Math.PI / 180; ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(cx, cy); ctx.lineTo(cx + maxR * 0.85 * Math.cos(predAng), cy + maxR * 0.85 * Math.sin(predAng)); ctx.strokeStyle = '#f0a500'; ctx.lineWidth = 2; ctx.setLineDash([4, 3]); ctx.stroke(); ctx.setLineDash([]); ctx.fillStyle = '#f0a500'; ctx.font = 'bold 9px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'center'; ctx.fillText('Pred. Wind', cx + maxR * 0.85 * Math.cos(predAng), cy + maxR * 0.85 * Math.sin(predAng) + 12); }
  [{ c: 'rgba(29,184,126,.6)', l: 'Valid + Freestream' }, { c: 'rgba(240,165,0,.5)', l: 'Partial' }, { c: 'rgba(231,76,60,.4)', l: 'Invalid' }].forEach((item, i) => { ctx.fillStyle = item.c; ctx.fillRect(10, H - 12 - i * 14, 10, 10); ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.4)'; ctx.font = '9px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'left'; ctx.fillText(item.l, 24, H - 2 - i * 14); });
}

function drawTerrainProfile(canvasId, sector) {
  const canvas = document.getElementById(canvasId); if (!canvas || !sector.profile || sector.profile.length === 0) return;
  const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d'), W = canvas.width, H = canvas.height, profile = sector.profile;
  ctx.clearRect(0, 0, W, H); ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(11,31,58,.5)'; ctx.fillRect(0, 0, W, H);
  const pad = { l: 55, r: 20, t: 25, b: 35 }, plotW = W - pad.l - pad.r, plotH = H - pad.t - pad.b;
  const maxDist = profile[profile.length - 1].dist;
  const elevs = profile.map(p => p.elev), minE = Math.min(...elevs), maxE = Math.max(...elevs), eRange = maxE - minE || 1;
  function toX(d) { return pad.l + (d / maxDist) * plotW; } function toY(e) { return pad.t + plotH - ((e - minE) / eRange) * plotH; }
  // Grid
  ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.06)'; ctx.lineWidth = 1;
  for (let i = 0; i <= 5; i++) { const x = pad.l + (plotW * i / 5); ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(x, pad.t); ctx.lineTo(x, H - pad.b); ctx.stroke(); }
  for (let i = 0; i <= 4; i++) { const y = pad.t + (plotH * i / 4); ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(pad.l, y); ctx.lineTo(W - pad.r, y); ctx.stroke(); ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.3)'; ctx.font = '9px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'right'; ctx.fillText((maxE - eRange * i / 4).toFixed(0) + 'm', pad.l - 5, y + 3); }
  // Slope thresholds
  const slopeThresh3 = eRange * 0.03 / (maxDist / profile.length) * 50;
  const slopeThresh10 = eRange * 0.10 / (maxDist / profile.length) * 50;
  // Terrain fill
  ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(toX(0), toY(profile[0].elev));
  for (const p of profile) ctx.lineTo(toX(p.dist), toY(p.elev));
  ctx.lineTo(toX(maxDist), H - pad.b); ctx.lineTo(toX(0), H - pad.b); ctx.closePath();
  ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(45,156,206,.12)'; ctx.fill();
  // Terrain line
  ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(toX(0), toY(profile[0].elev));
  for (const p of profile) ctx.lineTo(toX(p.dist), toY(p.elev));
  ctx.strokeStyle = '#2d9cce'; ctx.lineWidth = 2; ctx.stroke();
  // Labels
  ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.5)'; ctx.font = '9px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'center';
  for (let i = 0; i <= 5; i++) { ctx.fillText((maxDist * i / 5 / 1000).toFixed(1) + 'km', toX(maxDist * i / 5), H - pad.b + 15); }
  ctx.fillStyle = '#fff'; ctx.font = 'bold 11px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'left';
  ctx.fillText(`Sector ${sector.dir}° | Max Slope: ${sector.maxSlopeDeg.toFixed(1)}° | ${sector.terrainClass === 'A' ? 'Class A (Simple)' : sector.terrainClass === 'B' ? 'Class B (Complex)' : 'Class S (Very Complex)'}`, pad.l + 5, pad.t - 8);
  // Direction indicator
  ctx.fillStyle = sector.isFreestream ? 'rgba(29,184,126,.8)' : 'rgba(231,76,60,.8)';
  ctx.font = 'bold 10px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'right';
  ctx.fillText(sector.isFreestream ? 'FREESTREAM' : 'WAKE AFFECTED', W - pad.r - 5, pad.t - 8);
}

function renderFreestream() {
  if (!STATE.analysisResults || STATE.analysisResults.proposedMasts.length === 0) return;
  const m = STATE.analysisResults.proposedMasts[0];
  const mast = { id: m.name, name: m.name, lat: m.lat, lon: m.lon, height: m.height };
  const config = STATE.analysisResults.config;
  const a = performTerrainAssessment(mast, m.targetWTG, STATE.wtgs, STATE.extWtgs, STATE.terrainPoints, config);
  drawWakeRose('wakeRoseCanvas', a);
  document.getElementById('freestreamStats').innerHTML = `
    <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-val">${a.validCount}/${a.numSectors}</span><span class="stat-lbl">Valid Sectors</span></div>
    <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-val">${a.freestreamCount}/${a.numSectors}</span><span class="stat-lbl">Freestream</span></div>
    <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-val">${a.validPct.toFixed(0)}%</span><span class="stat-lbl">Valid %</span></div>
    <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-val">Class ${a.terrainClass}</span><span class="stat-lbl">Terrain</span></div>`;
  let html = '<table class="data-table"><thead><tr><th>Dir°</th><th>Freestream</th><th>Slope</th><th>Wake Sources</th><th>Valid</th></tr></thead><tbody>';
  for (const s of a.sectors) { html += `<tr><td>${s.dir}°</td><td>${s.isFreestream ? '✅' : '❌'}</td><td>${s.maxSlopeDeg.toFixed(1)}°</td><td>${s.wakeAffected.length > 0 ? s.wakeAffected.join(', ') : '—'}</td><td>${s.isValid ? '✅' : '❌'}</td></tr>`; }
  html += '</tbody></table>'; document.getElementById('wakeSectorTable').innerHTML = html;
}

function drawWakeRose(canvasId, assessment) {
  const canvas = document.getElementById(canvasId); if (!canvas) return;
  const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d'), W = canvas.width, H = canvas.height, cx = W / 2, cy = H / 2, maxR = Math.min(W, H) / 2 - 50;
  ctx.clearRect(0, 0, W, H); ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(11,31,58,0.5)'; ctx.beginPath(); ctx.arc(cx, cy, maxR + 10, 0, Math.PI * 2); ctx.fill();
  for (let r = 1; r <= 4; r++) { ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.06)'; ctx.beginPath(); ctx.arc(cx, cy, maxR * r / 4, 0, Math.PI * 2); ctx.stroke(); }
  ['N', 'NE', 'E', 'SE', 'S', 'SW', 'W', 'NW'].forEach((d, i) => { const ang = (i * 45 - 90) * Math.PI / 180; ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.4)'; ctx.font = '10px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'center'; ctx.textBaseline = 'middle'; ctx.fillText(d, cx + (maxR + 22) * Math.cos(ang), cy + (maxR + 22) * Math.sin(ang)); });
  const sectorAng = (2 * Math.PI) / assessment.numSectors;
  for (const s of assessment.sectors) {
    const sAng = (s.dir - 90) * Math.PI / 180 - sectorAng / 2, eAng = sAng + sectorAng;
    const color = s.isValid ? 'rgba(29,184,126,.5)' : s.isFreestream ? 'rgba(240,165,0,.5)' : 'rgba(231,76,60,.4)';
    const r = s.wakeAffected.length > 0 ? maxR * 0.6 : maxR * 0.9;
    ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(cx, cy); ctx.arc(cx, cy, r, sAng, eAng); ctx.closePath(); ctx.fillStyle = color; ctx.fill();
    if (s.wakeAffected.length > 0) { ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(231,76,60,.6)'; ctx.lineWidth = 1.5; ctx.stroke(); }
    else { ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(0,0,0,.2)'; ctx.lineWidth = 0.5; ctx.stroke(); }
  }
  if (STATE.analysisResults) { const predAng = (STATE.analysisResults.predDir - 90) * Math.PI / 180; ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(cx, cy); ctx.lineTo(cx + maxR * 0.85 * Math.cos(predAng), cy + maxR * 0.85 * Math.sin(predAng)); ctx.strokeStyle = '#f0a500'; ctx.lineWidth = 2.5; ctx.setLineDash([4, 3]); ctx.stroke(); ctx.setLineDash([]); }
  [{ c: 'rgba(29,184,126,.5)', l: 'Valid Sector' }, { c: 'rgba(240,165,0,.5)', l: 'Freestream (slope fail)' }, { c: 'rgba(231,76,60,.4)', l: 'Wake Affected' }].forEach((item, i) => { ctx.fillStyle = item.c; ctx.fillRect(10, H - 12 - i * 14, 10, 10); ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.4)'; ctx.font = '9px Open Sans'; ctx.textAlign = 'left'; ctx.fillText(item.l, 24, H - 2 - i * 14); });
}

function generateReport() {
  const r = STATE.analysisResults; if (!r) return;
  const best = r.proposedMasts[0]; const iec = document.getElementById('cfgIEC').value;
  let html = `
<h3>1. Executive Summary</h3>
<p>This report presents the results of a Power Curve Verification (PCV) site suitability assessment for a wind farm comprising <strong>${STATE.wtgs.length} target WTGs</strong>. ${STATE.extWtgs.length > 0 ? `${STATE.extWtgs.length} external WTGs from a neighboring wind farm were also considered for wake effects. ` : ''}The analysis follows IEC 61400-12-1:${iec} methodology to identify optimal met mast placement locations for PCV testing campaigns.</p>
<p>Predominant wind direction: <strong>${r.predDir}° (${degToCompass(r.predDir)})</strong>. Mean wind speed: <strong>${STATE.windRoseData.meanSpeed.toFixed(1)} m/s</strong>. ${r.firstRowWTGs.filter(w => w.isFirstRow).length} first-row WTGs were identified.</p>
${best ? `<p>The recommended primary mast location is <strong>${best.name}</strong> at coordinates <strong>(${best.lat.toFixed(1)}, ${best.lon.toFixed(1)})</strong>, targeting WTG <strong>${best.primary ? best.primary.name : best.targetWTG.name}</strong> at a distance of <strong>${best.distanceD.toFixed(1)}D (${best.distance.toFixed(0)}m)</strong>. Composite suitability score: <strong>${best.score}/100</strong>.</p>` : ''}

<h3>2. Wind Data Source</h3>
<table><tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Value</th></tr>
<tr><td>Data Source</td><td>${STATE.windData.length > 8000 ? 'ERA5T Reanalysis (Open-Meteo)' : 'Uploaded CSV'}</td></tr>
<tr><td>Records</td><td>${STATE.windData.length.toLocaleString()}</td></tr>
<tr><td>Mean Wind Speed</td><td>${STATE.windRoseData.meanSpeed.toFixed(1)} m/s</td></tr>
<tr><td>Predominant Direction</td><td>${r.predDir}° (${degToCompass(r.predDir)}) — ${STATE.windRoseData.predominant.frequency.toFixed(1)}%</td></tr>
<tr><td>Weibull K</td><td>${STATE.windRoseData.weibullK}</td></tr>
<tr><td>Calm Hours</td><td>${STATE.windRoseData.calmHours.toLocaleString()} (${STATE.windRoseData.calmPct.toFixed(1)}%)</td></tr></table>

<h3>3. First-Row WTG Identification</h3>
<p>Per IEC 61400-12-1, the test WTG should be a first-row turbine facing the predominant wind direction without upstream wake interference. Additionally, it should have a minimum free measurement sector of ${r.config.minFreeSector}° to ensure adequate data capture for power curve verification.</p>
<table><tr><th>WTG</th><th>First Row</th><th>Free Sector</th><th>Qualifies</th></tr>`;
  for (const w of r.firstRowWTGs) { const q = w.isFirstRow && w.freeSectorSpan >= r.config.minFreeSector; html += `<tr><td>${w.name}</td><td>${w.isFirstRow ? 'YES' : 'NO'}</td><td>${w.freeSectorSpan}°</td><td>${q ? 'YES' : 'NO'}</td></tr>`; }
  html += `</table>

<h3>4. Proposed Met Mast Locations</h3>
<p>The tool evaluated ${r.candidates.length} candidate positions at varying distances (${r.config.minDistanceD}D to 5D) upstream of qualifying first-row WTGs. After deduplication and scoring, ${r.proposedMasts.length} optimal mast locations are recommended.</p>
<table><tr><th>#</th><th>Mast ID</th><th>Coordinates</th><th>Target WTG</th><th>Distance</th><th>Valid Sectors</th><th>Terrain</th><th>Score</th></tr>`;
  r.proposedMasts.forEach((m, i) => { html += `<tr><td>${i + 1}</td><td>${m.name}</td><td>${m.lat.toFixed(1)}, ${m.lon.toFixed(1)}</td><td>${m.targetWTG.name}</td><td>${m.distanceD.toFixed(1)}D</td><td>${m.assessment.validCount}/${m.assessment.numSectors}</td><td>Class ${m.assessment.terrainClass}</td><td>${m.score}</td></tr>`; });
  html += `</table>

<h3>5. 1-Mast-to-2-WTG Configurations</h3>
<p>Where a proposed mast location can serve two WTGs with valid measurement sectors, a single mast can test both turbines, reducing campaign cost.</p>
<table><tr><th>Mast</th><th>Primary WTG</th><th>Secondary WTG</th><th>Combined Score</th></tr>`;
  for (const c of r.configs) { html += `<tr><td>${c.mast.name}</td><td>${c.primary.name}</td><td>${c.secondary ? c.secondary.name : '—'}</td><td>${c.score}</td></tr>`; }
  html += `</table>

<h3>6. IEC 61400-12-1 Compliance Parameters</h3>
<table><tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Value</th></tr>
<tr><td>IEC Standard</td><td>IEC 61400-12-1:${iec}</td></tr>
<tr><td>Sector Width</td><td>${r.config.sectorWidth}°</td></tr>
<tr><td>Assessment Radius</td><td>${r.config.assessmentRadius}m</td></tr>
<tr><td>Min Mast-WTG Distance</td><td>${r.config.minDistanceD}D</td></tr>
<tr><td>Wake Angular Threshold</td><td>${r.config.wakeAngularThreshold}°</td></tr>
<tr><td>Wake Distance Threshold</td><td>${r.config.wakeDistanceThresholdD}D</td></tr>
<tr><td>Min Free Sector</td><td>${r.config.minFreeSector}°</td></tr>
<tr><td>Terrain Has Real Data</td><td>${STATE.hasMapData ? 'Yes (.map file)' : 'No (synthetic terrain)'}</td></tr></table>

<h3>7. Recommendations</h3>`;
  for (const rec of r.recommendations) html += `<p>${rec}</p>`;
  document.getElementById('reportContent').innerHTML = html;
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
